(621, 5, '2015-12-11 00:19:07', '2015-12-11 00:19:07', '<h1 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Helping You Make Your House a Home</strong></h1>\r\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/people-1030750_1920.jpg"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/people-1030750_1920-300x200.jpg" alt="friends on a mission for Range Hoods" width="425" height="283" align="middle" /></a>\r\n\r\nWe are a group friends on a mission. A mission to make every kitchen a utopia. But why you ask? Think about it, Your kitchen is a central part of your home and your life. From preparing delicious meals and sharing them with your loved ones, to having quality conversations where important decisions and memories are made, all of these wonderful events take place in this special room we call the kitchen. It really should be your favorite room, and centered on what is truly important: Food, Family and Life.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'So, Who Are We Exactly?', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '594-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-11 00:19:07', '2015-12-11 00:19:07', '', 594, 'http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/?p=621', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
