(87, 1, '2015-08-14 18:05:00', '2015-08-14 18:05:00', '<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/no-bake-cake-batter-truffles-11.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-88 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/no-bake-cake-batter-truffles-11.jpg" alt="no bake cake batter truffles 1" width="1000" height="661" /></a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\nLooking for a quick and easy dessert recipe that is both festive and delicious? Do you love truffles as much as we do? Well look no further, because we have the perfect recipe for you, these No Bake - Cake Batter Truffles will leave your mouth watering and your guests coming back for more. You can easily make these in as little as 15-25 minutes with very little ingredients and no oven necessary! This is the perfect dessert to make for your kids, bring to a party, take into work, or best yet - to treat yourself with. After all, you deserve a little sweet treat every now and then!<!--more-->\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/no-bake-cake-batter-truffles-11.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-91 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/unnamed-3-e14395732212131.jpg" alt="unnamed-3" width="1000" height="563" /></a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/unnamed-e14395732011221.jpg"><img class=" wp-image-89 size-full aligncenter" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/unnamed-e14395732011221.jpg" alt="unnamed" width="1000" height="563" /></a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/unnamed-1-e14395732129461.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-90 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/unnamed-1-e14395732129461.jpg" alt="unnamed-1" width="1000" height="563" /></a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/unnamed-4-e14395732315111.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-92 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/unnamed-4-e14395732315111.jpg" alt="unnamed-4" width="1000" height="563" /></a>\n\n&nbsp;\n<p id="zlrecipe-ingredients" class="h-4 strong"><strong>Ingredients</strong></p>\n<p class="h-4 strong"><strong><span class="bold">For the Truffles:</span></strong></p>\n\n<ul id="zlrecipe-ingredients-list">\n	<li id="zlrecipe-ingredient-1" class="ingredient">1-1/2 c. flour</li>\n	<li id="zlrecipe-ingredient-2" class="ingredient">1 c. yellow cake mix</li>\n	<li id="zlrecipe-ingredient-3" class="ingredient">1/2 c. unsalted <span id="IL_AD11" class="IL_AD">butter</span>, softened</li>\n	<li id="zlrecipe-ingredient-4" class="ingredient">1/2 c. white sugar</li>\n	<li id="zlrecipe-ingredient-5" class="ingredient">1 tsp. vanilla</li>\n	<li id="zlrecipe-ingredient-6" class="ingredient">1/8 tsp. salt</li>\n	<li id="zlrecipe-ingredient-7" class="ingredient">3-4 tbsp. milk</li>\n	<li id="zlrecipe-ingredient-8" class="ingredient">2 tbsp. sprinkles</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong><span class="bold">For the Coating:</span></strong>\n<ul>\n	<li>16 oz. (8 squares) almond bark or vanilla flavored coating</li>\n	<li id="zlrecipe-ingredient-11" class="ingredient">Sprinkles</li>\n	<li id="zlrecipe-ingredient-12" class="ingredient">Pop sticks (for dipping)</li>\n</ul>\n<p id="zlrecipe-instructions" class="h-4 strong"><strong>Instructions</strong></p>\n\n<ol id="zlrecipe-instructions-list" class="instructions">\n	<li id="zlrecipe-instruction-0" class="instruction">For the truffles: Beat together butter and sugar using an electric mixer until combined. Add cake mix, flour, salt, and vanilla and mix thoroughly. Add 3–4 tbsp. of milk (I used 3) if needed to make a dough consistency. Mix in sprinkles by hand.</li>\n	<li id="zlrecipe-instruction-1" class="instruction"><span id="IL_AD1" class="IL_AD">Roll</span> dough into one-inch balls and place on parchment or wax paper on a cookie sheet. Chill balls in the <span id="IL_AD6" class="IL_AD">refrigerator</span> for 15 minutes to firm up.</li>\n	<li id="zlrecipe-instruction-2" class="instruction">For the coating: While dough balls are chilling, melt almond bark in the microwave in 30 second intervals until melted. Stir between intervals.</li>\n	<li id="zlrecipe-instruction-3" class="instruction">Using a pop stick, dip truffles into melted almond bark and gently twirl around to <span id="IL_AD12" class="IL_AD">remove</span>excess coating. Place truffle back on cookie sheet and top with sprinkles. Repeat with remaining balls until finished.</li>\n	<li id="zlrecipe-instruction-4" class="instruction">Chill truffles in the refrigerator until ready to serve.</li>\n	<li id="zlrecipe-instruction-5" class="instruction">Makes approximately <strong>24–30 truffles.</strong></li>\n</ol>\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RSOPdwxASLw&feature=youtu.be\n<p style="text-align: center;">We hope that you have enjoyed this Recipe! Let us know in the comments box below what you would like us to make next! Enjoy!</p>', 'No Bake - Cake Batter Truffles', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'no-bake-cake-batter-truffles', '', '', '2015-08-14 18:05:00', '2015-08-14 18:05:00', '', 0, 'http://directrangehoods.com/blog/?p=87', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(99, 1, '2015-08-17 16:42:38', '2015-08-17 16:42:38', '<p style="text-align: center;">Life can sometimes feel pretty hectic and these Kitchen tricks will help you to not only make your life easier, but also to become a better chef. With tricks like these cooking will be much more enjoyable and save you from spending too much time in the kitchen and more time at the table enjoying your loved ones.<!--more--></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Which Kitchen trick is your favorite? Let us know in the comments box below! Enjoy!</p>\n\n\n[caption id="attachment_100" align="aligncenter" width="1200"]<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/50hacks1.jpg"><img class="wp-image-100 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/50hacks1.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="11871" /></a> Photo Credit: <a href="http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/01/29/time-saving-cooking-hacks_n_6559384.html?ncid=edlinkushpmg00000055" target="_blank">Huffington Post</a>[/caption]\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>', '50 Culinary Hacks To Make You A Kitchen Master', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '50-culinary-hacks-to-make-you-a-kitchen-master', '', '', '2015-08-17 16:42:38', '2015-08-17 16:42:38', '', 0, 'http://directrangehoods.com/blog/?p=99', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(105, 1, '2015-08-18 18:28:48', '2015-08-18 18:28:48', '<p style="text-align: center;">We are so lucky to have so many wonderful customers who share pictures of their beautiful kitchens with us. This is one of our favorite customer kitchens featuring the <a href="http://directrangehoods.com/wall-range-hood-plfw-812.html" target="_blank">Proline PLFW 812 Range Hood. </a>This hood is versatile as it can be used as either a wall mounted range hood or as an under cabinet. It has a powerful 1,000-2,000 CFM blower and has one of the lowest noise settings in the industry.  It is not only efficient, but beautiful, with its stainless steel finish, unique shape, and modern design.<!--more--></p>\n&nbsp;\n\n<header id="header" class="page-header">\n<div class="page-header-container"></div>\n</header>\n<div class="innerwrapper">\n<div class="main-container col1-layout">\n<div class="main">\n<div class="col-main">\n<div id="messages_product_view"></div>\n<div class="product-view">\n<div class="product-essential"><form id="product_addtocart_form" action="http://directrangehoods.com/checkout/cart/add/uenc/aHR0cDovL2RpcmVjdHJhbmdlaG9vZHMuY29tL3dhbGwtcmFuZ2UtaG9vZC1wbGZ3LTgxMi5odG1s/product/466/form_key/ec7CVDJKPQanNamN/" method="post">\n<div class="spacer"></div>\n<div class="product-img-box">\n<div class="product-image product-image-zoom">\n<div class="product-image-gallery"><img id="image-main" class="gallery-image visible aligncenter" title="Professional Wall Mounted Range Hood -PLFW 812" src="http://directrangehoods.com/media/catalog/product/cache/9/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/l/plfw_812.36-i_2.png" alt="Professional Wall Mounted Range Hood -PLFW 812" /></div>\n<div class="product-image-gallery"></div>\n<div class="product-image-gallery"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</form></div>\n<div class="product-collateral toggle-content tabs"><dl class="collateral-tabs"><dd class="tab-container current">\n<div class="tab-content">\n<div class="std">\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>NOTE***</strong> These features may vary depending on the size selected. For more detailed information on each of the PLFW 812 model sizes please download the quick spec sheet <a title="Spec Sheet" href="http://proline-specs.com/html/proline_plfw_812-spec.html" target="_blank"><strong>HERE</strong></a>.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</dd></dl>\n<p style="text-align: center;">If you are remodeling your kitchen and looking for some great ideas, this is one kitchen that is sure to inspire. The mix of light walls and dark cabinets really creates some great contrast while enhancing the look and overall feel in this kitchen space. A great kitchen requires unique details and this white subway tile wall, and crown molding take this kitchen to a whole other level while really showing off the beautiful stainless steel range hood. This idea is perfect for someone who doesn''t like the look of a range hood chimney as it is fun way to hide the chimney, and enhance the space.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Screen-Shot-2015-08-18-at-10.32.06-AM2.jpg"><img class=" wp-image-106 size-full aligncenter" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Screen-Shot-2015-08-18-at-10.32.06-AM2.jpg" alt="Screen Shot 2015-08-18 at 10.32.06 AM" width="1983" height="2647" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center;">The warmer tones in this kitchen create a feeling of comfort while the lighter and brighter colors add a vibrance, and overall cheerfulness to the space. The rug pulls both the light and dark colors together nicely and adds a classy detail, as well as a nice place to stand for long hours of cooking.<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Screen-Shot-2015-08-18-at-10.32.12-AM1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-107 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Screen-Shot-2015-08-18-at-10.32.12-AM1.jpg" alt="Screen Shot 2015-08-18 at 10.32.12 AM" width="1972" height="2650" /></a>\nThe under cabinet lighting is also a favorite feature as it helps provide beautiful bright light while cooking and sets a relaxing mood in this kitchen.\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Screen-Shot-2015-08-18-at-10.32.12-AM1.jpg">\n</a>We hope that by sharing customer kitchens that you will feel inspired, get unique ideas for your kitchen space, and gain a better understanding of the quality and style of our range hoods. After all, the kitchen is the heart of the home, and the range hood is the center of the kitchen. Let us know in the comments box below what you think about this customer kitchen!</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>', 'Customer Kitchen Remodel: Proline PLFW 812 Range Hood', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'customer-kitchen-remodel-proline-plfw-812-range-hood', '', '', '2015-08-18 18:28:48', '2015-08-18 18:28:48', '', 0, 'http://directrangehoods.com/blog/?p=105', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(120, 1, '2015-08-19 21:44:27', '2015-08-19 21:44:27', 'Summer is almost coming to an end and there’s only one fabulous way to celebrate: an outdoor dining soiree! Let''s face it. You’ve been waiting for just about any excuse to plan a party at your place. Prepping the table is only half the fun, whether you’re planning a picnic style luncheon or wanting your guests to get dressed up for an elegant dinner celebration. Breathe a sigh of relief — because we’ve found all of the inspiration you need to style a stunning table. Now send out the invites, have a few friends over, pour some fruity drinks and get ready to soak up the sun while you get your grub on.\n<div></div>\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674348 aligncenter" src="http://pixel.brit.co/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/preppy-pink.jpg" alt="" width="645" height="880" data-pin-no-hover="true" />\n\n1. <a href="http://www.inspiredbythis.com/wed/inspired-by-these-citrus-orange-pink-wedding-ideas/" target="_blank">Preppy Orange and Pink</a>: A table gets pretty with pop of bright colors and patterns. Get creative, and have fun with the bold colors. They’ll add that instant wow factor. (via <a href="http://www.inspiredbythis.com/wed/inspired-by-these-citrus-orange-pink-wedding-ideas/" target="_blank">Inspired By This</a>)\n<div></div>\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674352 aligncenter" src="http://pixel.brit.co/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/chevron-runner.jpg" alt="" width="645" height="970" data-pin-no-hover="true" />\n\n2. <a href="http://www.stylemepretty.com/gallery/picture/589554/" target="_blank">Chevron Table Runner</a>: Want to transform a table from blah to ahh? All you will need is one defining table runner — like this stunning pink and gold chevron style. (via <a href="http://www.stylemepretty.com/gallery/picture/589554/" target="_blank">Style Me Pretty</a>)\n<div></div>\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674367 aligncenter" src="http://pixel.brit.co/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/PICNIC-BOX.jpg" alt="" width="645" height="881" data-pin-no-hover="true" />\n\n3. <a href="http://www.erickelleyphotography.com/blog/?p=5162" target="_blank">Picnic Box Place Setting</a>: Suddenly we’re totally inspired to have a picnic. These packed lunches and colorful napkins are too cute for words.  This is one picnic we are not going to miss. (via <a href="http://www.erickelleyphotography.com/blog/?p=5162" target="_blank">Eric Kelley Photography</a>)\n<div></div>\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674394 aligncenter" src="http://pixel.brit.co/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/preppy-stripes.jpg" alt="" width="645" height="866" data-pin-no-hover="true" />\n\n4. <a href="http://www.mysweetandsaucy.com/" target="_blank">Preppy Stripes</a>: The secret ingredient to an instantly stunning tablescape is simple: stripes! It’s the cutest design for just about any table setting, but we’re particularly in love with the way bright colors pop in this print-worthy photo. (via <a href="http://www.mysweetandsaucy.com/" target="_blank">My Sweet + Saucy</a>)\n<div></div>\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674364 aligncenter" src="http://pixel.brit.co/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/vintage-carnival.jpg" alt="" width="645" height="969" data-pin-no-hover="true" />\n\n5. <a href="http://ruffledblog.com/carnival-theme-wedding/" target="_blank">Vintage Carnival Inspiration</a>: Green apples at each place setting are eye candy. Eat up! (via <a href="http://ruffledblog.com/carnival-theme-wedding/" target="_blank">Ruffled</a>)\n<div></div>\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674399 aligncenter" src="http://pixel.brit.co/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/wooden-table-runner.jpg" alt="" width="645" height="968" data-pin-no-hover="true" />\n\n6.<a href="http://www.100layercake.com/blog/2013/11/11/autumn-dinner-party/" target="_blank"> Wooden Table Runner</a>: How rad is this color blocked wooden table runner? You could totally DIY the runner to coordinate perfectly with your party colors. (via <a href="http://www.100layercake.com/blog/2013/11/11/autumn-dinner-party/" target="_blank">100 Layer Cake</a>)\n<div></div>\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674354 aligncenter" src="http://pixel.brit.co/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/surf-inspired.jpg" alt="" width="645" height="770" data-pin-no-hover="true" />\n\n7. <a href="http://greenweddingshoes.com/" target="_blank">Surf Inspired Tablescape</a>: We’re done with stuffy dinner parties. Kick back and keep things comfy and cool by seating your guests on soft pillows next to a low table. A colorful tassel garland makes the scene a bit more festive. It’s party time! (via <a href="http://greenweddingshoes.com/" target="_blank">Green Wedding Shoes</a>)\n<div></div>\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674363 aligncenter" src="http://pixel.brit.co/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/farm-inspired-table.jpg" alt="" width="645" height="969" data-pin-no-hover="true" />\n\n8. <a href="http://www.stylemepretty.com/living/2014/04/09/farm-to-table-entertaining/" target="_blank">Farm Inspired Table</a>: A rustic farm-style table is transformed with the addition of wildflower bouquets, kraft paper placemats and gold votive candles. (via <a href="http://www.stylemepretty.com/living/2014/04/09/farm-to-table-entertaining/" target="_blank">Style Me Pretty</a>)\n<div></div>\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674359 aligncenter" src="http://pixel.brit.co/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Orange-Crush-Tablescape.jpg" alt="" width="645" height="426" data-pin-no-hover="true" />\n\n9. <a href="http://greenweddingshoes.com/orange-crush-wedding-inspiration/" target="_blank">Orange Crush Tablescape</a>: Next up: inspiration for a mood-boosting party! Your guests <em>won’t</em> be disappointed to discover that dinner’s on the patio with this irresistible orange table-setting. (via <a href="http://greenweddingshoes.com/orange-crush-wedding-inspiration/" target="_blank">Green Wedding Shoes</a>)\n<div></div>\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674347 aligncenter" src="http://pixel.brit.co/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/simple-white.jg_.jpg" alt="" width="645" height="968" data-pin-no-hover="true" />\n\n10. <a href="http://alowcountrywedding.blogspot.com/2012/01/every-tuesday-we-like-to-give-all-of.html" target="_blank">Simple White Place Setting</a>: Taking the party outside doesn’t mean that you have to eat with paper plates and plastic cutlery. Keep things simple, yet stylish with a monochromatic setting and a single flower. (via <a href="http://alowcountrywedding.blogspot.com/2012/01/every-tuesday-we-like-to-give-all-of.html" target="_blank">A LowCountry Wedding</a>)\n<div></div>\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674358 aligncenter" src="http://pixel.brit.co/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/dotty.jpg" alt="" width="645" height="430" data-pin-no-hover="true" />\n\n11. <a href="http://bklynbrideonline.com/30136/wedding-flowers/donna-wilson-inspired-tablescape-with-diy-planters/" target="_blank">Dotty Table With DIY Planters</a>: DIY this table for your next outdoor fete. You’ll garner bragging rights when you surprise your guests by passing out the planters as parting favors. (via <a href="http://bklynbrideonline.com/30136/wedding-flowers/donna-wilson-inspired-tablescape-with-diy-planters/" target="_blank">Brooklyn Bride</a>)\n<div></div>\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674362 aligncenter" src="http://pixel.brit.co/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/garland.jpg" alt="" width="645" height="881" data-pin-no-hover="true" />\n\n12. <a href="http://www.stylemepretty.com/gallery/picture/1354438/" target="_blank">Table-Length Garland</a>: Looking for something a bit more elegant? A long table-length garland steals the show without being too fussy. Add some taper candles to balance out the centerpiece perfectly. (via <a href="http://www.stylemepretty.com/gallery/picture/1354438/" target="_blank">Style Me Pretty</a>)\n<div></div>\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674357 aligncenter" src="http://pixel.brit.co/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/wooden-board-table-runner.jpg" alt="" width="645" height="968" data-pin-no-hover="true" />\n\n13. <a href="http://www.weddingchicks.com/2013/02/13/roloff-farms-wedding/" target="_blank">Wood Plank Table Runner</a>: Mason jars <a href="http://www.brit.co/mason-jars/" target="_blank">aren’t going away any time soon</a>. Plop some pretty flowers into hand-painted jars atop a rustic wood plank for an instant centerpiece. The horizontal napkin placing is another lovely touch and a great way to style each plate without covering up the menu. (via <a href="http://www.weddingchicks.com/2013/02/13/roloff-farms-wedding/" target="_blank">Wedding Chicks</a>)\n<div></div>\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674365 aligncenter" src="http://pixel.brit.co/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/bottle-candles.jpg" alt="" width="645" height="968" data-pin-no-hover="true" />\n\n14. <a href="http://twitpic.com/9w462x" target="_blank">Bottle Candleholders</a>: Hurry! Snatch all the glass bottles from your recycling tub, they’re gonna be put to good use. (via <a href="http://twitpic.com/9w462x" target="_blank">Twitpic</a>)\n<div></div>\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674486 aligncenter" src="http://pixel.brit.co/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/terra-cotta.jpg" alt="" width="645" height="959" data-pin-no-hover="true" />\n\n15. <a href="http://www.stylemepretty.com/gallery/picture/904991/" target="_blank">Terracotta Pots Centerpiece</a>: Sometimes we’re busy. Or maybe just plain lazy. Whatever the case, we want a trendy table in a hurry, minimal cost, minimal fuss. Those potted plants hanging around your front porch? They’ll do perfectly. (via <a href="http://www.stylemepretty.com/gallery/picture/904991/" target="_blank">Style Me Pretty</a>)\n<div></div>\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674349 aligncenter" src="http://pixel.brit.co/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/wildflowers.jpg" alt="" width="645" height="968" data-pin-no-hover="true" />\n\n16. <a href="http://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=6220&amp;awinaffid=233801&amp;clickref=&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fetsy.com%2Fblog%2Fweddings%2Freal-weddings-garden-soiree%2F" target="_blank" rel="noskim" data-affiliate-link="">Fresh Wildflowers With a Vintage Vibe</a>: It’s all about the details — pretty prints, pint jars, wildflowers, stripy straws and even a bit of burlap. This summery mix of southern charm and vintage prints is exactly what makes us want to get in on the fun. Invite us! (via <a href="http://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=6220&amp;awinaffid=233801&amp;clickref=&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fetsy.com%2Fblog%2Fweddings%2Freal-weddings-garden-soiree%2F" target="_blank" rel="noskim" data-affiliate-link="">Etsy Weddings</a>)\n<div></div>\n<img class=" size-full wp-image-677271 aligncenter" title="glitz" src="http://pixel.brit.co/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/glitz1.jpg" alt="" width="645" height="862" data-pin-no-hover="true" />\n\n17. <a href="http://www.weddingchicks.com/2012/02/14/red-and-pink-wedding-ideas/" target="_blank">Glitz and Glamour</a>: Sick of the same old table setting? We hear ya. What you need is a good dose of glam. Glitter never goes out of style. And there’s no better way to break out of boring. (via <a href="http://www.weddingchicks.com/2012/02/14/red-and-pink-wedding-ideas/" target="_blank">Wedding Chicks</a>)\n<div></div>\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674488 aligncenter" src="http://pixel.brit.co/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/peonies.jpg" alt="" width="645" height="928" data-pin-no-hover="true" />\n\n18. <a href="http://www.stylemepretty.com/2010/07/06/from-inspiration-to-wedding-the-photography/" target="_blank">Pretty Peonies</a>: Your next backyard bash can be completely charming with the simple addition of a few peonies. (via <a href="http://www.stylemepretty.com/2010/07/06/from-inspiration-to-wedding-the-photography/" target="_blank">Style Me Pretty</a>)\n<div></div>\n<img class="size-full wp-image-674361 aligncenter" src="http://pixel.brit.co/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/succulent.jpg" alt="" width="645" height="968" data-pin-no-hover="true" />\n\n19. <a href="http://www.stylemepretty.com/2010/07/06/from-inspiration-to-wedding-the-photography/" target="_blank">Simple Succulent Place Setting</a>: Succulents are all the rage. Not only are they beautiful, but they are virtually indestructible. <a href="http://www.brit.co/b/succulent-planter/" target="_blank">Make a bunch of these mini potted versions</a> to grace each guest’s place, and they’ll be thrilled to take it home afterward. (via <a href="http://www.stylemepretty.com/2010/07/06/from-inspiration-to-wedding-the-photography/" target="_blank">Ruffled</a>)\n<div></div>\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674351 aligncenter" src="http://pixel.brit.co/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/crates.jpg" alt="" width="645" height="953" data-pin-no-hover="true" />\n\n20. <a href="http://www.brides.com/wedding-ideas/wedding-style/2013/10/vineyard-wedding-style-decor-ideas#slide=14" target="_blank">Rustic Wine Crate Centerpieces</a>: What’s not to love about these adorable wine crate centerpieces? It’s an easy way to add rustic charm to a table. (via <a href="http://www.brides.com/wedding-ideas/wedding-style/2013/10/vineyard-wedding-style-decor-ideas#slide=14" target="_blank">Brides</a>)\n<div></div>\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674369 aligncenter" src="http://pixel.brit.co/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/fresh-herbs.jpg" alt="" width="645" height="660" data-pin-no-hover="true" />\n\n21. <a href="http://www.styleathome.com/food-and-entertaining/party-planner/11-tips-for-a-backyard-garden-party/a/51339" target="_blank">Potted Herbs Centerpieces</a>: Show your friends that you were into pretty napkins, burlap and potted herbs before Pinterest ever made them a thing. (via <a href="http://www.styleathome.com/food-and-entertaining/party-planner/11-tips-for-a-backyard-garden-party/a/51339" target="_blank">Style at Home</a>)\n<div></div>\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674350 aligncenter" src="http://pixel.brit.co/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/citrus.jpg" alt="" width="645" height="860" data-pin-no-hover="true" />\n\n22. <a href="http://apartment34.com/2013/05/let-the-grand-summer-begin/" target="_blank">Simple Citrus Setting</a>: Can we all agree that any event involving this amount of citrus is something we want in on? This centerpiece is pretty enough to… well, eat. If you don’t want your guests dipping into the fruit bowl, you might want to add a piece of fruit to each place setting. (via <a href="http://apartment34.com/2013/05/let-the-grand-summer-begin/" target="_blank">Apartment 34</a>)\n<div></div>\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674346 aligncenter" src="http://pixel.brit.co/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/sunflowers.jpg" alt="" width="645" height="970" data-pin-no-hover="true" />\n\n23. <a href="http://www.weddingchicks.com/gallery/footloose-themed-engagement-party/?nggpage=4&amp;pid=69867" target="_blank">Sunflower Setting</a>: Here comes the sun… flowers. Brighten up an alfresco meal with the addition of these yellow babies and napkins in coordinating colors. It’s not too fancy, just peppy and plain fun. (via <a href="http://www.weddingchicks.com/gallery/footloose-themed-engagement-party/?nggpage=4&amp;pid=69867" target="_blank">Wedding Chicks</a>)\n<div></div>\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674360 aligncenter" src="http://pixel.brit.co/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/peachy-sweetjpg.jpg" alt="" width="645" height="880" data-pin-no-hover="true" />\n\n24. <a href="http://www.stylemepretty.com/2013/09/02/farewell-to-summer-photo-shoot-from-ruth-eileen-photography/" target="_blank">Peachy Sweet</a>: Why not bring the kitchen table into the yard along with some pretty dinnerware? We love that eating outside can be so glam. (via <a href="http://www.stylemepretty.com/2013/09/02/farewell-to-summer-photo-shoot-from-ruth-eileen-photography/" target="_blank">Style Me Pretty</a>)\n<div></div>\n<img class=" size-full wp-image-676072 aligncenter" src="http://pixel.brit.co/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/gingham1.jpg" alt="" width="645" height="429" data-pin-no-hover="true" />\n\n25. <a href="http://iloveswmag.com/" target="_blank">Gingham Style</a>: Why not go gingham? So fun, we’re ready to break into song and dance. Oppa Gingham style! (via <a href="http://iloveswmag.com/" target="_blank">Southern Weddings Mags</a>)\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>What’s on your outdoor party table? Talk to us about your favorite table settings in the comments box below!</strong></p>', '25 Table Settings to Inspire Your Next Dinner Party', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '25-table-settings-to-inspire-your-next-dinner-party', '', '', '2015-08-19 21:44:27', '2015-08-19 21:44:27', '', 0, 'http://directrangehoods.com/blog/?p=120', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(126, 1, '2015-08-20 18:12:17', '2015-08-20 18:12:17', '<p style="text-align: center;">When you are on the go, sometimes you just need a few quick recipes that you can count on. Thats why we have searched to find our top 5 favorite recipes that are not only quick but healthy and delicious. Let us know in the comments box below which one is your favorite. Enjoy!</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>1) <a href="http://pinchofyum.com/simple-poached-egg-avocado-toast" target="_blank">Poached E</a></strong><a href="http://pinchofyum.com/simple-poached-egg-avocado-toast" target="_blank"><strong>gg and Avocado toast -via Pinch of Yum</strong></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Once you try Avocado toast, you will be hooked. It''s not only healthy, but also delicious, and EASY!</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://pinchofyum.com/simple-poached-egg-avocado-toast" target="_blank"><strong><img class="aligncenter wp-image-127 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/poached-egg-toast-32.jpg" alt="poached-egg-toast-3" width="600" height="887" /></strong></a></p>\n\n<div style="text-align: left;"></div>\n<div style="text-align: left;"></div>\n<div style="text-align: left;"></div>\n<div style="text-align: left;"><strong>2) <a href="http://www.gimmesomeoven.com/crunchy-asian-ramen-noodle-salad/" target="_blank">Crunchy Asian Ramen Noodle Salad -via Gimme Some Oven</a></strong></div>\n<div style="text-align: left;">A healthy and delicious lunch that will be done in SNAP. Delicious vegetables piled on top of ramen noodles, we are convinced that this dish will be your new favorite.</div>\n<div style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Crunchy-Asian-Ramen-Salad-71.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-128 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Crunchy-Asian-Ramen-Salad-71.jpg" alt="Crunchy-Asian-Ramen-Salad-7" width="576" height="864" /></a></div>\n<div style="text-align: left;"></div>\n<div style="text-align: left;"></div>\n<div style="text-align: left;"><strong>3) <a href="http://lovegrowswild.com/2013/09/spicy-cilantro-shrimp-with-honey-lime-dipping-sauce/" target="_blank">Spicy Cilantro Shrimp With Honey Lime Dipping Sauce -via Love Grows Wild</a></strong></div>\n<div style="text-align: left;">If you like a little bit of Zing to your meals, this dish was made for you. This Spicy Shrimp Recipe will blow your tastebuds in all of the right ways.</div>\n<div style="text-align: left;"></div>\n<div style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Spicy-Cilantro-Shrimp-Honey-Lime-Dipping-Sauce-91.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-129 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Spicy-Cilantro-Shrimp-Honey-Lime-Dipping-Sauce-91.jpg" alt="Spicy-Cilantro-Shrimp-Honey-Lime-Dipping-Sauce-9" width="427" height="640" /></a></div>\n<div style="text-align: left;"></div>\n<div style="text-align: left;"></div>\n<div style="text-align: left;"></div>\n<div style="text-align: left;"><strong>4) <a href="http://skinnyms.com/spinach-bean-burrito-wrap/" target="_blank">Spinach and Bean Burrito Wrap -via Skinny Ms.</a></strong></div>\n<div style="text-align: left;">Perfect for breakfast, Lunch, or Dinner. This burrito recipe is not only healthy, but packed with flavor.</div>\n<div style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Spinach-Bean-Burrito-Wrap1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-130 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Spinach-Bean-Burrito-Wrap1.jpg" alt="Spinach-Bean-Burrito-Wrap" width="600" height="478" /></a></div>\n<div style="text-align: left;"></div>\n<div style="text-align: left;"></div>\n<div style="text-align: left;"></div>\n<div style="text-align: left;"><strong>5) <a href="http://damndelicious.net/2012/11/07/lightened-up-greek-yogurt-chicken-salad-sandwich/" target="_blank">Greek Yogurt Chicken Salad Sandwich via-Damn Delicious</a></strong></div>\n<div style="text-align: left;">Thats right- this sandwich involves NO MAYO, just greek yogurt. If you are looking for a healthy delicious sandwich that is flavorful and packed with proteins, fruits and veggies, you need to try this!</div>\n<div style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Greek-Yogurt-Chicken-Salad-Sandwich1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-131 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Greek-Yogurt-Chicken-Salad-Sandwich1.jpg" alt="Greek-Yogurt-Chicken-Salad-Sandwich" width="650" height="975" /></a></div>', '5 Easy 10 Minute Healthy Recipes To Make When You Are On The Go', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '5-easy-10-minute-healthy-recipes-to-make-when-you-are-on-the-go', '', '', '2015-08-20 18:12:17', '2015-08-20 18:12:17', '', 0, 'http://directrangehoods.com/blog/?p=126', 0, 'post', '', 0);
