(135, 1, '2015-08-24 16:09:39', '2015-08-24 16:09:39', '&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center;">Back to school mornings are here and we know many of times they can feel pretty hectic.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Although it''s still important to make sure that everyone has meal to start their busy mornings. Breakfast is a great meal to set the right tone to anyones day and that is why we searched the web to find 10 recipes that everyone will love.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/French-Toast-Kabobs-The-Foodie-Affair1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-136 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/French-Toast-Kabobs-The-Foodie-Affair1.jpg" alt="French-Toast-Kabobs-The-Foodie-Affair" width="1024" height="683" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.thefoodieaffair.com/2014/02/04/french-toast-fruit-kabobs/" target="_blank">French Toast Fruit Kabobs: The Foodie Affair</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Chocolate-Banana-Muffins1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-137 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Chocolate-Banana-Muffins1.jpg" alt="Chocolate-Banana-Muffins" width="700" height="1050" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.chef-in-training.com/2014/09/chocolate-banana-muffins/" target="_blank">Chocolate Banana Muffins: Chef-in-Training</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/60cb6f26-93cf-4d0f-b91b-be1dcc5154901.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-138 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/60cb6f26-93cf-4d0f-b91b-be1dcc5154901.jpg" alt="60cb6f26-93cf-4d0f-b91b-be1dcc515490" width="800" height="450" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.bettycrocker.com/r