8/Nutella-Strawberry-and-Banana-Waffles-1024x6831.jpg" alt="Nutella-Strawberry-and-Banana-Waffles-1024x683" width="1024" height="683" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.addicted2recipes.com/2015/02/nutella-strawberry-and-banana-waffles/" target="_blank">Nutella Strawberry and Banana Waffles: Addicted 2 Recipes</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Eggs-smoked-salmon2-HERO-3aa17bda-a708-44eb-af01-0a03467fc151-0-472x3101.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-144 " src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Eggs-smoked-salmon2-HERO-3aa17bda-a708-44eb-af01-0a03467fc151-0-472x3101.jpg" alt="Eggs-smoked-salmon2-HERO-3aa17bda-a708-44eb-af01-0a03467fc151-0-472x310" width="981" height="487" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://realfood.tesco.com/recipes/deluxe-scrambled-eggs-with-smoked-salmon-chives-and-spring-onion.html" target="_blank">Deluxe Scrambled Eggs with With Smoked Salmon Chives and Spring Onion: RealFood</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/c7def6bf-d737-46cc-befd-12fdb991e4fe1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-145 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/c7def6bf-d737-46cc-befd-12fdb991e4fe1.jpg" alt="c7def6bf-d737-46cc-befd-12fdb991e4fe" width="900" height="602" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://amillionmiless.com/2014/12/timekeeping-acai-bowls/" target="_blank">TimeKeeping Acai Bowls: A Million Miles</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/blat-31.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-146 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/blat-31.jpg" alt="blat-3" width="668" height="775" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.howsweeteats.com/2013/03/avocado-blts