(189, 1, '2015-09-01 16:30:40', '2015-09-01 16:30:40', '<p style="text-align: center;">Happy first day of September!</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Even though the first day of fall is technically not until September 23rd, pumpkin season is just about here and we thought we would celebrate early! We have searched to find our very favorite pumpkin recipes for fall, and we are sharing them with you! Have you heard of a Pumpkin Soft Pretzel or ever tried Pumpkin Cheesecake bites? Take a peak at some of our favorite finds and let us know which one you want to try in the comments box below! Enjoy! Don''t forget to subscribe for more recipes and beautiful kitchen ideas to be sent straight to your inbox.</p>\n<p class="aligncenter" style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/cinnamon-sugar-pumpkin-pretzels-42.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-191 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/cinnamon-sugar-pumpkin-pretzels-42.jpg" alt="cinnamon-sugar-pumpkin-pretzels-4" width="680" height="1020" /></a>\n<a href="http://lecremedelacrumb.com/2014/09/cinnamon-sugar-pumpkin-soft-pretzels.html" target="_blank">Cinnamon Sugar Pumpkin Soft Pretzels- Creme De La Crumb</a></p>\n<p class="aligncenter" style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Pumpkin-Swirled-Cheesecakes1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-192 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Pumpkin-Swirled-Cheesecakes1.jpg" alt="Pumpkin-Swirled-Cheesecakes" width="600" height="1267" /></a></p>\n<p class="aligncenter" style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://omgchocolatedesserts.com/pumpkin-swirled-cheesecakes/" target="_blank">Pumpkin Swirled Mini Cheesecakes - OMG Chocolate Desserts</a></p>\n<p class="aligncenter" style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/pumpkincinnrolls-221.jpg