le fudge!" width="629" height="930" data-pin-url="http://www.averiecooks.com/2014/06/thick-and-fudgy-chocolate-peanut-butter-smoothie.html" data-jpibfi-indexer="9" /></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="title"><a title="Pineapple Mango Vitamin C Booster Smoothie" href="http://www.averiecooks.com/2013/03/pineapple-mango-vitamin-c-booster-smoothie.html" rel="bookmark">Pineapple Mango Vitamin C Booster Smoothie</a> (vegan, GF) – Work in extra Vitamin C with this smooth, creamy, easy and healthy smoothie!</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter" title="Pineapple Mango Vitamin C Booster Smoothie (vegan, GF) averiecooks.com" src="http://cdn.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/pineapplebooster-22.jpg" alt="Pineapple Mango Vitamin C Booster Smoothie (vegan, GF) averiecooks.com" width="585" height="800" data-pin-url="http://www.averiecooks.com/2013/09/skinny-pina-colada-smoothie.html" data-jpibfi-indexer="10" /></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="title"><a title="Cherry Revitalizer Smoothie + KitchenAid Stand Mixer + LeCreuset Dutch Oven Go Tart Giveaway" href="http://www.averiecooks.com/2014/02/cherry-revitalizer-smoothie-kitchenaid-stand-mixer-lecreuset-dutch-oven-go-tart-giveaway.html" rel="bookmark">Cherry Revitalizer Smoothie</a>  (vegan, GF) – Gives you energy and leaves you feeling refreshed and revitalized! </span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-45499" title="Cherry Revitalizer Smoothie (vegan, GF) - Gives you energy and leaves you feeling refreshed and revitalized! " src="http://cdn.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/cherryrevitalizertext.jpg" alt="Cherry Revitalizer Smoothie (vegan, GF) - Gives you energy and leaves you feeling refreshed and revitalized! " width="630" height="925" data-pin-url="http://www.averiecooks.com/2014/07/watermelon-raspberry-slushies.html" data-jpibfi-indexer="11" /></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="title"><a title="Spiced Apple Pie Smoothie" href="http://www.averiecooks.com/2012/02/spiced-apple-pie-smoothie.html" rel="bookmark">Spiced Apple Pie Smoothie</a> (vegan, GF) – Sweet, creamy and a perfect way to use your apples!</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-16127" title="Spiced Apple Pie Smoothie (vegan, GF) - Sweet, creamy &amp; you know what they say...An apple pie smoothie a day keeps the doctor away!" src="http://cdn.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/applepiesmoothie-15.jpg" alt="Spiced Apple Pie Smoothie (vegan, GF) - Sweet, creamy &amp; you know what they say...An apple pie smoothie a day keeps the doctor away!" width="546" height="800" data-pin-url="http://www.averiecooks.com/2012/02/spiced-apple-pie-smoothie.html" data-jpibfi-indexer="12" /></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="title"><a title="Blueberry Banana Recovery Smoothie" href="http://www.averiecooks.com/2011/10/blueberry-banana-recovery-smoothie.html" rel="bookmark">Blueberry Banana Recovery Smoothie</a> – Sweet, fruity, a little bit creamy, and very refreshing! A great post-workout smoothie!</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-11380 size-full" title="blueberrysmoothie-9" src="http://cdn.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/blueberrysmoothie-9.jpg" alt="Blueberry Banana Recovery Smoothie - Sweet, fruity, a little bit creamy, and very refreshing! A great post-workout smoothie!" width="555" height="800" data-pin-url="http://www.averiecooks.com/2011/10/blueberry-banana-recovery-smoothie.html" data-jpibfi-indexer="13" /></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="title"><a title="Coconut Cream Pie Smoothie" href="http://www.averiecooks.com/2012/08/coconut-cream-pie-smoothie.html" rel="bookmark">Coconut Cream Pie Smoothie</a> (vegan, GF) – Tastes like a slice of coconut cream pie! Creamy, smooth, and no sugar added!</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter" title="Coconut Cream Pie Smoothie (vegan, GF) - Tastes like a slice of coconut cream pie! Creamy, smooth, &amp; no sugar added!" src="http://cdn.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/coconutcreamsmoothiewords.jpg" alt="Coconut Cream Pie Smoothie (vegan, GF) - Tastes like a slice of coconut cream pie! Creamy, smooth, &amp; no sugar added!" width="598" height="800" data-pin-url="http://www.averiecooks.com/2012/08/coconut-cream-pie-smoothie.html" data-jpibfi-indexer="14" /></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="title"><a title="Skinny Caramel Frappuccino" href="http://www.averiecooks.com/2013/06/skinny-caramel-frappuccino.html" rel="bookmark">Skinny Caramel Frappuccino</a> – Move over Starbucks, this version only has 50 calories per serving! Thinks of all the money (and calories) you’ll save by making your own!</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-37939" title="Skinny Caramel Frappuccino - Only 50 Calories Per Serving - Recipe at averiecooks.com" src="http://cdn.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/caramelfrappuccino-19.jpg" alt="Skinny Caramel Frappuccino - Only 50 Calories Per Serving - Recipe at averiecooks.com" width="561" height="850" data-pin-url="http://www.averiecooks.com/2013/06/skinny-caramel-frappuccino.html" data-jpibfi-indexer="15" /></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="Berry Greens Vanilla Smoothie" href="http://www.averiecooks.com/2015/01/berry-greens-vanilla-smoothie.html">Berry Greens Vanilla Smoothie</a> – Healthy, easy, and tastes amazing!! You’d never guess it’s packed with greens and so good FOR you!</p>\n<img class="wp-image-53736 size-large aligncenter" src="http://cdn.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/berrygreenssmoothietext2-630x920.jpg" alt="Berry Greens Vanilla Smoothie - Healthy, easy, and tastes amazing!! You''d never guess it''s packed with greens and so good FOR you!!" width="630" height="920" data-pin-url="http://www.averiecooks.com/2015/01/berry-greens-vanilla-smoothie.html" data-jpibfi-indexer="16" />', '15 QUICK & EASY HEALTHY SMOOTHIE RECIPES', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '15-quick-easy-healthy-smoothie-recipes', '', '', '2015-09-08 17:18:34', '2015-09-08 17:18:34', '', 0, 'http://directrangehoods.com/blog/?p=231', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(235, 1, '2015-09-09 21:36:07', '2015-09-09 21:36:07', '<p style="text-align: center;">Cheers to the best time of year as the cooler weather quickly comes upon us.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Why is it that we love this Fall season so much?</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">It may just be the gentle whistling  sound the wind makes coming through your window, or listening to the leaves crash together as you quietly read in your cozy corner, sipping hot chocolate under a warm blanket beside the fire. Maybe its the excitement you feel for Pumpkin season and being able to light as many Pumpkin scented candles around your house while you make fresh Pumpkin Chocolate chip cookies or a batch of homemade Pumpkin bread.  mmm-mmmm.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">The sunshine has treated us well and Summer has been a breeze, but we are jumping with excitement for beautiful Autumn season for another excuse to cozy up our homes.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">We are so excited that we have found 8 ways to cozy up your house for Fall and we are sharing these fabulous finds with you!</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">1) Add a Faux Fur throw to your favorite Lounge spot. Not only will this add an elegant touch, but a very cozy one.</p>\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/67daf2e267362e05c27daa3c218f23081.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-236" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/67daf2e267362e05c27daa3c218f23081-300x300.jpg" alt="" width="635" height="680" /></a>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.mmphotoart.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;" target="_blank">Photo Styling by Magdalena Martin</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">2) Candles all day everyday.  We recommend finding real flame burning candles that make your house smell like you are always up to no good baking. You could also add some flameless candles in your fire place to make a beautiful center display.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/bf02470fd72ea282c57ab0fc6d81390f1.jpg"><img class="alignnone  wp-image-239" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/bf02470fd72ea282c57ab0fc6d81390f1-300x300.jpg" alt="bf02470fd72ea282c57ab0fc6d81390f" width="611" height="611" /></a>    <a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/58f5986957fcf6b9e2094818345e25201.jpg"><img class="alignnone  wp-image-240" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/58f5986957fcf6b9e2094818345e25201-300x300.jpg" alt="58f5986957fcf6b9e2094818345e2520" width="615" height="615" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Candles from <a href="http://Bath and Body Works" target="_blank">Bath and Body Works</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">3) Spruce up your doorstep. Nothing says Autumn like a fun Fall Wreath. Add some pumpkins along the walkway to really make grand entrance.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/3ffe22fffbf9cc8812936b153dc629992.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-242 " src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/3ffe22fffbf9cc8812936b153dc629992.jpg" alt="3ffe22fffbf9cc8812936b153dc62999" width="617" height="926" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Photo Credit: <a href="http://www.fourgenerationsoneroof.com/2014/09/gorgeous-front-door-fall-decorating-ideas.html" target="_blank">Four Generations One Roof</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/e3d81f5e6a6364f703c829aa7ac5a21d1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-243 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/e3d81f5e6a6364f703c829aa7ac5a21d1.jpg" alt="e3d81f5e6a6364f703c829aa7ac5a21d" width="736" height="988" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Photo Credit: <a href="http://www.serendipityrefined.com/2014/09/fall-harvest-porch-decor-with-reclaimed.html" target="_blank">Serendipity Refined</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">4) Pumpkins GALORE. Work those pumpkins on your mantel, on your doorstep, or even as a centerpiece on your table. Don''t by shy, have some fun, even make some pumpkin pie while your at it.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/a214a9d1ba094e673e9aa1ab37f7e6541.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-244 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/a214a9d1ba094e673e9aa1ab37f7e6541.jpg" alt="a214a9d1ba094e673e9aa1ab37f7e654" width="600" height="745" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Photo Credit: <a href="http://www.bystephanielynn.com/2011/09/10-tips-for-purchasing-caring-for-fall-mums-my-tuesday-ten-no-14.html">bystephanielynn.com</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/65b4c585500c95f7417b4df19ba9f4d81.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-245 " src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/65b4c585500c95f7417b4df19ba9f4d81.jpg" alt="65b4c585500c95f7417b4df19ba9f4d8" width="549" height="808" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Photo Credit: <a href="http://www.homedit.com/30-thanksgiving-table-setting-ideas-for-a-festive-decor-celebration/">homedit.com</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">6) Change up your Mantel. Hang a sign, change up the amount  of space used by mixing both big scale decor items with small scale items.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1ba1f76eb11bd226717945769a889c041.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-246 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1ba1f76eb11bd226717945769a889c041.jpg" alt="1ba1f76eb11bd226717945769a889c04" width="560" height="787" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Photo Credit: <a href="http://thefrugalhomemaker.com/2013/10/01/31-days-fall-inspiration-fall-mantel/">thefrugalhomemaker.com</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">7) Leaves and Pinecones. Find a good quality bow of leaves and some pinecones at your local craft or home store and make a display on the center of your table of along your mantel.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/222c8e81769884231b82c776e49239f71.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-247 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/222c8e81769884231b82c776e49239f71.jpg" alt="222c8e81769884231b82c776e49239f7" width="620" height="827" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Photo Credit: <a href="http://www.topinspired.com/top-10-creative-diy-thanksgiving-decorations/"> topinspired.com</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/2494227b977e99dd4579bf089d2d36471.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-248 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/2494227b977e99dd4579bf089d2d36471.jpg" alt="2494227b977e99dd4579bf089d2d3647" width="640" height="960" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Photo Credit: <a href="http://www.bohemianandchic.com/articulo/20-detalles-decorativos-hechos-con-arpillera-20-decoratives-details-made-burlap">bohemianandchic.com</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">8) Change up your throw pillows. If you are not a fan of warmer fall colors, then incorporate cooler tones and just change up your fabrics to softer, more comfortable ones.  If you do not have the budget to change your couch pillows every season, then get out of your comfort zone and simply make them! Find the color scheme and fabrics that you want and start sewing! Before you know it you will become the best Do-It-Yourselfer in town.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/5e5961bee610e25719b97cd6723185911.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-249 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/5e5961bee610e25719b97cd6723185911.jpg" alt="5e5961bee610e25719b97cd672318591" width="584" height="879" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Photo Credit: <a href="http://lujo.co.nz/blogs/lujo-inspiration-blog/12691085-creating-a-cosy-autumn-home">lujo.co.nz</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Hopefully these ideas have helped you get inspired to get your home ready for Fall. Let us know which one of these ideas is your favorite in the comments box below! Thanks for stopping by! Don''t forget to subscribe!</p>', '8 Ways to Cozy Up Your House for Fall', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '8-ways-to-cozy-up-your-house-for-fall', '', '', '2015-09-09 21:36:07', '2015-09-09 21:36:07', '', 0, 'http://directrangehoods.com/blog/?p=235', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(253, 1, '2015-09-14 22:06:23', '2015-09-14 22:06:23', '<p style="text-align: center;">We believe in beautiful, and functional kitchens. We also believe that the your kitchen should be your favorite part of your home. After all, a family that eats together and cooks together stays together right?</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">When you look at the kitchen as a whole, you may not realize it but the range hood actually plays a major role as it is considered to be the centerpiece of the kitchen.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">So what are you waiting for? Show off that range hood! Turn up the heat. Here are 10 Range Hood Ideas that are HOT this season. Let us know which of these design ideas is your favorite in the the comments box below. While you are at it, SUBSCRIBE to be up-to-date with the most delicious recipes, kitchen inspiration, culinary tips, entertaining ideas and more. Happy Monday!</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">1) <strong>Tile Over it - </strong>Really show off that range hood by tiling over it. This will give your vent hood a great structure component and a simple elegance that is sure to make a statement.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/kitchen-kitchen-trends-51.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-256 " src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/kitchen-kitchen-trends-51.jpg" alt="kitchen-kitchen-trends-5" width="628" height="893" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Photo Credit: <a href="http://www.styleathome.com/kitchen-and-bath/trends/2014-kitchen-design-trends/a/54303/5" target="_blank">Style At Home</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">2) <strong>Get Creative With the Backsplash. </strong>Take the tile to the ceiling, try a more decorative tile design or keep it simple and clean with a white subway tile design. Maybe you want a more commercial look and are wanting a stainless steel backsplash, or possibly you consider your style to be more modern and are looking for a clean glass slab. Whatever you find tickles your fancy, play up that backsplash as it truly does amazing things for your range hood.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1017065102.jpg.rendition.largest2.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-258 " src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1017065102.jpg.rendition.largest2.jpg" alt="101706510.jpg.rendition.largest" width="628" height="799" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Photo Credit: <a href="http://www.bhg.com/kitchen/backsplash/kitchen-backsplash-ideas/#page=2" target="_blank">Better Homes and Gardens</a><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/kitchen_11.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-259 " src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/kitchen_11.jpg" alt="kitchen_1" width="632" height="795" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Photo Credit: <a href="http://interiorsbystudiom.com/herringbone-pattern-mosaic-tile-wood-flooring/" target="_blank">Interiorsbystudiom.com</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">3) <strong>Build It in.</strong> Traditional homes have shown that building in the range hood is one of the best ways to show it off. Its kind of like putting your favorite picture into a beautiful frame. Give your vent hood that little extra character and charm by adding just a little more glam to your kitchen space. <a href="http://directrangehoods.com/range-hood-inserts.html" target="_blank">Take a look at our range hood insert selection HERE</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/3110a4e5b1d1357ea8d569bd780a74a31.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-260 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/3110a4e5b1d1357ea8d569bd780a74a31.jpg" alt="3110a4e5b1d1357ea8d569bd780a74a3" width="642" height="874" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Photo Credit: <a href="http://Found on homebunch.com" target="_blank">HomeBunch.com</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/e24e99bf478549a4bc22b7cd1fe495cc1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-261 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/e24e99bf478549a4bc22b7cd1fe495cc1.jpg" alt="e24e99bf478549a4bc22b7cd1fe495cc" width="736" height="981" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Photo C: <a href="http://photos.hgtv.com/photo/white-transitional-kitchen-with-marble-countertops" rel="nofollow" data-element-type="27">Found on photos.hgtv.com</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">4) <strong>Work the Stainless Steel. </strong>When it comes to range hoods, stainless steel is classic, easy to clean and not to mention- gorgeous. Just when you thought you couldn''t be a bigger fan, you will find out that stainless steel range hoods  are also one of the most affordable options when looking for high quality kitchen ventilation.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/hood-copy1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-264 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/hood-copy1.jpg" alt="hood copy" width="855" height="575" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/IMG_00401.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-263 " src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/IMG_00401-1024x768.jpg" alt="IMG_0040" width="845" height="595" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/image11.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-262 " src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/image11-1024x768.jpg" alt="image1" width="833" height="561" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Photo Credits</strong>: All three kitchen spaces are real customer kitchens.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">5) <strong>Custom Carved Range Hood. </strong>Nothing says luxurious quite like a custom carved wooden range hood does.<a href="http://directrangehoods.com/bradshaw-french-country-wall-hood.html" target="_blank"> Check out our new Bradshaw French Country Model from our Artisan Series HERE.</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/IMG_03681.jpg"><img class="alignnone wp-image-265 " src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/IMG_03681-1024x683.jpg" alt="IMG_0368" width="816" height="572" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://directrangehoods.com/bradshaw-french-country-wall-hood.html" target="_blank">Bradshaw French Country Model from our Artisan Series</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">6) <strong>Go Big. </strong>Maybe you consider yourself a chef boss and want your kitchen to be a grand-slam with luxurious, large scale kitchen appliances. Go for that commercial restaurant style kitchen with a mighty grand sized range hood. Who knew kitchen ventilation could add such a fun detail for a space?<img class="aligncenter wp-image-269 " src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/e2a97755ef730557bab2d597fd4583801.jpg" alt="e2a97755ef730557bab2d597fd458380" width="701" height="819" /></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Photo Credit: <a href="http://decoracion.facilisimo.com/blogs/general/cocinas-grises-top-25_944119.html" rel="nofollow" data-element-type="27">decoracion.facilisimo.com</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">7)<strong> Replace that microwave.  </strong>It has been proven that microwave ventilation does not cover nearly enough stove top space, nor is it as effective as clearing the air as range hood ventilation. There are always options for places to put your microwave whether thats down below in a slide out drawer, built in your cabinets, or on top of your counter space. We may be biased but we feel range hoods also make kitchen spaces extra beautiful.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/kitchenrangepin1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-270 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/kitchenrangepin1.jpg" alt="kitchenrangepin" width="676" height="1000" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Check out this DIY Mantel Range Hood Tutorial: <a href="http://www.goldenboysandme.com/2014/01/diy-mantel-hood-tutorial.html" target="_blank">Golden Boys and Me</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">8) <strong>Decorate it.</strong> Use some decorative brackets to spice things up or add a ledge above your hood in order to really dress it up with fun decor items for the different seasons.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/f8032586d2135dddd533a250196789d31.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-271 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/f8032586d2135dddd533a250196789d31.jpg" alt="f8032586d2135dddd533a250196789d3" width="685" height="1028" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Photo Credit:<a href="http://pinkpeonies.com/home-holidays/" rel="nofollow" data-element-type="27"> pinkpeonies.com</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">9) <strong>Iron Hoods. </strong>Nothing makes a statement like a good strong Iron Range Hood. Whether you like the farmhouse look, industrial, modern, or traditional, an Iron hood will surely make your kitchen say LOOK AT ME. Check out our <a href="http://directrangehoods.com/innovative-iron.html" target="_blank">Innovative French Iron Hood</a>, our <a href="http://directrangehoods.com/innovative-iron-craftsman-under-cabinet-hood.html" target="_blank">Iron Square Craftsman Under Cabinet Hood</a>, and our <a href="http://directrangehoods.com/innovative-iron-victorian-under-cabinet-hood.html" target="_blank">Innovative Iron-Rounded Victoria Under Cabinet Hood</a> from our Artisan series.</p>\n\n\n[caption id="attachment_266" align="aligncenter" width="605"]<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/iron-11.jpg"><img class="wp-image-266 size-large" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/iron-11-1024x905.jpg" alt="" width="605" height="535" /></a> <a href="http://Craftsman Under Cabinet Hood" target="_blank">Craftsman Under Cabinet Hood</a>[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_267" align="aligncenter" width="611"]<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/iron-hood-21.jpg"><img class="wp-image-267" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/iron-hood-21-1024x992.jpg" alt="" width="611" height="608" /></a> <a href="http://Innovative French Iron Hood" target="_blank">Innovative French Iron Hood</a>[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_268" align="aligncenter" width="747"]<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Iron-hood-31.jpg"><img class="wp-image-268" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Iron-hood-31-1024x810.jpg" alt="" width="747" height="586" /></a> <a href="http://Innovative Iron-Rounded Victoria Under Cabinet Hood" target="_blank">Innovative Iron-Rounded Victoria Under Cabinet Hood</a>[/caption]\n<p style="text-align: center;">10) <strong>Paint it. </strong>Do you love color? Are you going for a more shabby-chic style or an eccentric look and want your range hood to match your other aqua sky blue appliances? Get your range hood painted! Add that pop of color to your kitchen in a snap. Easy as that.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/0965251ff0bcb0a882633afac7ea2b6a1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-272 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/0965251ff0bcb0a882633afac7ea2b6a1.jpg" alt="0965251ff0bcb0a882633afac7ea2b6a" width="550" height="733" /></a>Photo Credit:<a href="http://www.bhg.com/kitchen/backsplash/cheap-backsplash-ideas/" rel="nofollow" data-element-type="27">bhg.com</a></p>\n&nbsp;', 'Turn Up The Heat.10 Range Hood Ideas That are HOT This Season.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'turn-up-the-heat-10-range-hood-ideas-that-are-hot-this-season', '', '', '2015-09-14 22:06:23', '2015-09-14 22:06:23', '', 0, 'http://directrangehoods.com/blog/?p=253', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(276, 1, '2015-09-17 20:34:40', '2015-09-17 20:34:40', '<p style="text-align: center;">Football Season is here and that means you need some game day snack ideas pronto for the big game this weekend!</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Whether you are in the mood for some cheesy, crispy Mozzarella Sticks, or a some delicious burgers. We''ve got you covered! We have gathered our very favorite 11 Game Day recipes to share with the objective to help you  get your tailgating weekend started off right. A party with good food, and good football? Count Us In!</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Let us know your favorites in the comments box below along with your favorite game day treat! Enjoy!</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/cheesesticks-5-731x1024-11.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-277 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/cheesesticks-5-731x1024-11.jpg" alt="cheesesticks-5-731x1024-1" width="731" height="1024" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">1) Crispy Wonton Mozzarella Sticks - <a href="http://neighborfoodblog.com/2013/09/crispy-wonton-mozzarella-sticks.html" target="_blank">Neighbor Food Blog</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Totchos-Supreme-Burgers-42.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-278 " src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Totchos-Supreme-Burgers-42.jpg" alt="Totchos-Supreme-Burgers-4" width="726" height="961" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"> 2) <a href="http://www.halfbakedharvest.com/totchos-supreme-burgers/" target="_blank">Totchos Supreme Burgers - Half Baked Harvest</a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/enhanced-11701-1410370884-201.png"><img class="alignnone wp-image-279 " src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/enhanc