(299, 1, '2015-09-24 21:55:03', '2015-09-24 21:55:03', '<p style="text-align: center;">Have you ever been to a luxurious restaurant or a friends house where you were treated to an incredibly outstanding food plate that just looked like it should be put in a museum because it was almost too pretty to eat?</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"> Nothing is more impressive or appealing than a well composed plate of delicious food. Even the professional chef bosses take years perfecting this skill so that we may go crazy over their food masterpieces. Making a delicious meal takes serious skill, but to master the overall arrangement and styling on top takes lots of effort, planning, creativity, talent, and expertise in the culinary world.  As humans we tend to feast with our eyes first, and that''s why we have found some of our favorite culinary masterpieces in order to share some serious food styling inspiration with you.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Are you a food boss and make creations like this everyday? Share your favorites with us or photos of your own food art in the comments box below. Bon Appetite!</p>\n\n<header class="entry-header">\n<div class="entry-meta"></div>\n</header>\n<div class="entry-content" style="text-align: center;">\n\n<a href="http://i.telegraph.co.uk/multimedia/archive/02213/keller-food_2213599c.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-3271" src="https://livingxdesign.files.wordpress.com/2014/02/d3e8b45a1363260bcee8785dc6a69b0b.jpg?w=500&amp;h=311" alt="d3e8b45a1363260bcee8785dc6a69b0b" width="809" height="503" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://chefs-talk.com/people/Yann_Bernard_Lejard"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-3273" src="https://livingxdesign.files.wordpress.com/2014/02/46e8e211dfa22b0cd0879a0af703caf5.jpg?w=500&amp;h=633" alt="46e8e211dfa22b0cd0879a0af703caf5" width="797" height="1009" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://lopezdezubiria.com/files/gimgs/18_33322.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-3274" src="https://livingxdesign.files.wordpress.com/2014/02/d0f54c549c839ffe674ce18d43e21c3c.jpg?w=1000&amp;h=562" alt="d0f54c549c839ffe674ce18d43e21c3c" width="980" height="549" /></a>Brushstrokes of sauce, spare use of colors in food.\n\n<strong>The tower</strong> – piling ingredients, one on top of another.\n\n<img class="aligncenter wp-image-3275" src="https://livingxdesign.files.wordpress.com/2014/02/04ae349b25b6320ee4fd0829900dfcb6.jpg?w=1000&amp;h=776" alt="04ae349b25b6320ee4fd0829900dfcb6" width="1009" height="783" />\n\n<a href="http://www.seasons.nl/2012/overig/exclusief-librije-recept-van-jonnie-boer/"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-3276" src="https://livingxdesign.files.wordpress.com/2014/02/1e5e65f3a3b83bbe42da2858f879df45.jpg?w=500&amp;h=565" alt="1e5e65f3a3b83bbe42da2858f879df45" width="830" height="938" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/foodandwineholidays/7973417/The-Cote-dAzurs-Michelin-stars.html"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-3277" src="https://livingxdesign.files.wordpress.com/2014/02/b714b8931d2be8409e203a42b6b5a806.jpg?w=500&amp;h=313" alt="b714b8931d2be8409e203a42b6b5a806" width="760" height="476" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://miamivisual.com/"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-3293" src="https://livingxdesign.files.wordpress.com/2014/02/6d23abe551c634adae1a6475318ffd78.jpg?w=500&amp;h=746" alt="6d23abe551c634adae1a6475318ffd78" width="748" height="1116" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://www.gallinablanca.es/receta/bacalao-con-patatas-alioli-de-manzana-y-transparencia-de-miel/?utm_source=pinterest"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-3278" src="https://livingxdesign.files.wordpress.com/2014/02/c571c7004dc778e92e42e28393a2fc9e.jpg?w=1000&amp;h=1310" alt="c571c7004dc778e92e42e28393a2fc9e" width="721" height="943" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://thebitesizedblog.com/blog/2010/05/19/seared-tuna-wth-avocado-citrus-and-lotus-root/#.Uv2xrGJdWfa"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-3286" src="https://livingxdesign.files.wordpress.com/2014/02/38650dcac107781b42d7131ccc0e201c.jpg?w=500&amp;h=615" alt="38650dcac107781b42d7131ccc0e201c" width="716" height="881" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/originals/fc/4d/c6/fc4dc604d652a567e99ccebd105cd72b.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-3287" src="https://livingxdesign.files.wordpress.com/2014/02/fc4dc604d652a567e99ccebd105cd72b.jpg?w=500&amp;h=500" alt="fc4dc604d652a567e99ccebd105cd72b" width="728" height="728" /></a>Always top the tower off with something eye catching!\n\nSome food just want to be <strong>the lone island.</strong>\n\n<a href="http://www.guillaumeczerw.com/#/images_culinaire_8/1"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-3279" src="https://livingxdesign.files.wordpress.com/2014/02/986164616187ee1b07eefe6480f6cd9c.jpg?w=1000&amp;h=1500" alt="986164616187ee1b07eefe6480f6cd9c" width="786" height="1177" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://www.zencancook.com/2012/02/turbans-of-langoustines-with-shellfish-consomme-bottarga/"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-3296" src="https://livingxdesign.files.wordpress.com/2014/02/39930549adff400626caa9b6353dc59f.jpg?w=500&amp;h=751" alt="39930549adff400626caa9b6353dc59f" width="736" height="1105" /></a>\n\n<img class="aligncenter  wp-image-3280" src="https://livingxdesign.files.wordpress.com/2014/02/725baba2e381a0dfef39d841b4cd2f09.jpg?w=500&amp;h=511" alt="725baba2e381a0dfef39d841b4cd2f09" width="713" height="729" />\n\n<a href="http://media-cache-ec0.pinimg.com/originals/16/0a/77/160a77cc76141d2388779e07b366a847.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-3281" src="https://livingxdesign.files.wordpress.com/2014/02/160a77cc76141d2388779e07b366a847.jpg?w=1000&amp;h=1002" alt="160a77cc76141d2388779e07b366a847" width="797" height="797" /></a>\n\n<strong>The spring garden-</strong> gather a concoction of greens and bright colors.\n\n<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/nicolefranzen/12324575914/sizes/l/in/photostream/"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-3282" src="https://livingxdesign.files.wordpress.com/2014/02/7ff5976a9af8c8a924c4a874defeb074.jpg?w=500&amp;h=749" alt="7f