(638, 1, '2015-12-23 17:57:52', '2015-12-23 17:57:52', '<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Holiday-Dessert-Tools.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-639 size-large" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Holiday-Dessert-Tools-1024x678.jpg" alt="Tools for Holiday Desserts" width="1024" height="678" /></a>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">The Holidays are here and that means it''s baking Season!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Need a good neighbor gift? A Killer Dessert Recipe for a the Annual Christmas Family Party? Or are you just in the Christmas spirit and craving a holiday treat for you and your loved ones?</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Well you are in the right place! We have rounded up all of our favorites, and we are excited to share them with you! Enjoy!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">1. <a href="http://thefoodcharlatan.com/2014/12/19/candy-cane-brownie-trifle/" target="_blank">Candy Cane Brownie Trifle -The Food Charlatan</a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_640" align="aligncenter" width="648"]<a href="http://thefoodcharlatan.com/2014/12/19/candy-cane-brownie-trifle/" target="_blank" rel="attachment wp-att-640"><img class="wp-image-640 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/3a366f1015c947dfec02756839e9c3cf-e1450722688711.jpg" alt="Candy Cane Brownie Trifle" width="648" height="936" /></a> Courtesy of The Food Charlatan[/caption]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">2.<a href="http://www.somethingswanky.com/better-than-christmas-poke-cake/">Better Than Christmas Poke Cake - Something Swanky</a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n[caption id="" align="aligncenter" width="600"]<a href="http://www.somethingswanky.com/better-than-christmas-poke-cake/" target="_blank"><img src="http://i2.wp.com/www.somethingswanky.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/DSC_2096-edited-watermarked.png?resize=600%2C896" alt="Better than Christmas Poke Cake" width="600" height="896" />