(704, 5, '2016-01-29 17:41:43', '2016-01-29 17:41:43', '<p style="text-align: center;">Just because Summer has come to an end doesn''t mean that your goals for eating healthy and staying fit should end too. That is why we have found 15 quick and easy healthy smoothie recipes for you to try to stay on track!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Each of these smoothies are healthy and skinny-jean friendly.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Let us know which smoothie recipe you want to try along with your own favorite healthy smoothie recipe in the comments box below! Enjoy!\r\n<img class="aligncenter wp-image-53684 size-full" src="http://averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/smoothiescollage.jpg" alt="The Best 15 Healthy Smoothies -  Fast, easy, and tasty smoothie recipes that''ll keep you full and satisfied and are skinny jeans-friendly! " width="630" height="1890" data-jpibfi-indexer="0" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span id="more-53683"></span><a title="Skinny Pina Colada Smoothie" href="http://www.averiecooks.com/2013/09/skinny-pina-colada-smoothie.html" rel="bookmark">Skinny Pina Colada Smoothie</a> (vegan, GF) – Under 100 calories for a creamy, rich &amp; satisfying smoothie that tastes like the real deal!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-40207" title="Skinny Pina Colada Smoothie (vegan, gluten-free) - Under 100 Calories - Easy Recipe at averiecooks.com" src="http://cdn.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/pinacoladasmoothie-16.jpg" alt="Skinny Pina Colada Smoothie (vegan, gluten-free) - Under 100 Calories - Easy Recipe at averiecooks.com" width="605" height="875" data-pin-url="http://www.averiecooks.com/2013/09/skinny-pina-colada-smoothie.html" data-jpibfi-indexer="1" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="title"><a title="Strawberries and Cream Smoothie" href="http://www.averiecooks.com/2012/03/strawberries-and-cream-smoothie.html" rel="bookmark">Strawberries and Cream Smoothie</a> (vegan, GF) –  Like a strawberry milkshake but healthier! Sweet, creamy and satisfying!</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-17982" title="Strawberries and Cream Smoothie (vegan, GF) - Like a strawberry milkshake but healthier! Sweet, creamy &amp; satisfying!" src="http://cdn.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/strawberriescream-3.jpg" alt="Strawberries and Cream Smoothie (vegan, GF) - Like a strawberry milkshake but healthier! Sweet, creamy &amp; satisfying!" width="565" height="800" data-pin-url="http://www.averiecooks.com/2012/03/strawberries-and-cream-smoothie.html" data-jpibfi-indexer="2" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="title"><a title="Tropical Green Smoothie" href="http://www.averiecooks.com/2013/03/tropical-green-smoothie.html" rel="bookmark">Tropical Green Smoothie</a> (vegan, GF) – Tastes like a Pina Colada. Sweet, creamy, healthy and gives me more energy than coffee!</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter" title="Tropical Green Smoothie (vegan, GF) averiecooks.com" src="http://cdn.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/greensmoothie-10.jpg" alt="Tropical Green Smoothie (vegan, GF) averiecooks.com" width="617" height="800" data-pin-url="http://www.averiecooks.com/2013/03/tropical-green-smoothie.html" data-jpibfi-indexer="3" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="Blueberry Pie Smoothie" href="http://www.averiecooks.com/2014/03/blueberry-pie-smoothie.html">Blueberry Pie Smoothie</a> (vegan, GF) – A healthy, no-sugar-added smoothie that tastes like a blueberry pie! So good!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-46187" title="Blueberry Pie Smoothie (vegan, GF) - A healthy, no-sugar-added smoothie that tastes like a blueberry pie! So good!" src="http://cdn.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/blueberrypiesmoothietext1.jpg" alt="Blueberry Pie Smoothie (vegan, GF) - A healthy, no-sugar-added smoothie that tastes like a blueberry pie! So good!" width="630" height="850" data-pin-url="http://www.averiecooks.com/2014/03/blueberry-pie-smoothie.html" data-jpibfi-indexer="4" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.averiecooks.com/2014/04/strawberry-banana-pineapple-smoothie.html">Strawberry Banana Pineapple Smoothie</a> (vegan, GF) – No sugar needed in this refreshing, 3-ingredient, healthy smoothie!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="pibfi_pinterest"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-47672" title="Strawberry Banana Pineapple Smoothie (vegan, GF) - No sugar needed in this refreshing, 3-ingredient, healthy smoothie!" src="http://cdn.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/strawbananasmoothietext1.jpg" alt="Strawberry Banana Pineapple Smoothie (vegan, GF) - No sugar needed in this refreshing, 3-ingredient, healthy smoothie!" width="630" height="925" data-pin-url="http://www.averiecooks.com/2012/03/strawberries-and-cream-smoothie.html" data-jpibfi-indexer="5" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="Tropical Peach Pineapple Slushies" href="http://www.averiecooks.com/2014/05/tropical-peach-pineapple-slushies.html" rel="bookmark">Tropical Peach Pineapple Slushies</a> – No added sugar! Cool, refreshing and they go down so easily! Optionally add alcohol and makes a great party drink.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-48584 size-full" src="http://cdn.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/peachpineappleslushiestext.jpg" alt="Tropical Peach Pineapple Slushies - Plenty of booze &amp; no added sugar, a win-win! Cool, refreshing &amp; they go down so easily!" width="630" height="950" data-pin-url="http://www.averiecooks.com/2014/05/tropical-peach-pineapple-slushies.html" data-jpibfi-indexer="6" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="title"><a title="Watermelon Raspberry Slushies" href="http://www.averiecooks.com/2014/07/watermelon-raspberry-slushies.html" rel="bookmark">Watermelon Raspberry Slushies</a> –  Cool, refreshing, and you’ll want a refill before you know it! Optionally add alcohol and get the party started.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-50354 size-full" src="http://cdn.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/watermelonslushiestext.jpg" alt="Watermelon Raspberry Slushies - Summertime in a glass! Cool, refreshing, and you''ll want a refill before you know it!" width="630" height="959" data-pin-url="http://www.averiecooks.com/2014/07/watermelon-raspberry-slushies.html" data-jpibfi-indexer="7" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="title"><a title="Pineapple Banana &amp; Coconut Cream Smoothie" href="http://www.averiecooks.com/2011/12/pineapple-banana-coconut-cream-smoothie.html" rel="bookmark">Pineapple Banana &amp; Coconut Cream Smoothie</a> (vegan, GF) – Tastes like a virgin pina colada. Sweet, creamy, refreshing and healthy! No need to add sugar since the fruit is sweet enough!</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-14504" src="http://cdn.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/pineapplebanana-6.jpg" alt="" width="542" height="800" data-pin-url="http://www.averiecooks.com/2011/12/pineapple-banana-coconut-cream-smoothie.html" data-jpibfi-indexer="8" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="title"><a title="Thick and Fudgy Chocolate Peanut Butter Smoothie" href="http://www.averiecooks.com/2014/06/thick-and-fudgy-chocolate-peanut-butter-smoothie.html" rel="bookmark">Thick and Fudgy Chocolate Peanut Butter Smoothie</a> (vegan, GF) – You’ll need a spoon for this smoothie that tastes like drinkable fudge!</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-49326 size-full" src="http://cdn.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/chocpbsmoothietext.jpg" alt="Thick and Fudgy Chocolate Peanut Butter Smoothie (vegan, GF) - You''ll need a spoon for this smoothie that tastes like drinkable fudge!" width="629" height="930" data-pin-url="http://www.averiecooks.com/2014/06/thick-and-fudgy-chocolate-peanut-butter-smoothie.html" data-jpibfi-indexer="9" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="title"><a title="Pineapple Mango Vitamin C Booster Smoothie" href="http://www.averiecooks.com/2013/03/pineapple-mango-vitamin-c-booster-smoothie.html" rel="bookmark">Pineapple Mango Vitamin C Booster Smoothie</a> (vegan, GF) – Work in extra Vitamin C with this smooth, creamy, easy and healthy smoothie!</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter" title="Pineapple Mango Vitamin C Booster Smoothie (vegan, GF) averiecooks.com" src="http://cdn.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/pineapplebooster-22.jpg" alt="Pineapple Mango Vitamin C Booster Smoothie (vegan, GF) averiecooks.com" width="585" height="800" data-pin-url="http://www.averiecooks.com/2013/09/skinny-pina-colada-smoothie.html" data-jpibfi-indexer="10" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="title"><a title="Cherry Revitalizer Smoothie + KitchenAid Stand Mixer + LeCreuset Dutch Oven Go Tart Giveaway" href="http://www.averiecooks.com/2014/02/cherry-revitalizer-smoothie-kitchenaid-stand-mixer-lecreuset-dutch-oven-go-tart-giveaway.html" rel="bookmark">Cherry Revitalizer Smoothie</a>  (vegan, GF) – Gives you energy and leaves you feeling refreshed and revitalized! </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-45499" title="Cherry Revitalizer Smoothie (vegan, GF) - Gives you energy and leaves you feeling refreshed and revitalized! " src="http://cdn.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/cherryrevitalizertext.jpg" alt="Cherry Revitalizer Smoothie (vegan, GF) - Gives you energy and leaves you feeling refreshed and revitalized! " width="630" height="925" data-pin-url="http://www.averiecooks.com/2014/07/watermelon-raspberry-slushies.html" data-jpibfi-indexer="11" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="title"><a title="Spiced Apple Pie Smoothie" href="http://www.averiecooks.com/2012/02/spiced-apple-pie-smoothie.html" rel="bookmark">Spiced Apple Pie Smoothie</a> (vegan, GF) – Sweet, creamy and a perfect way to use your apples!</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-16127" title="Spiced Apple Pie Smoothie (vegan, GF) - Sweet, creamy &amp; you know what they say...An apple pie smoothie a day keeps the doctor away!" src="http://cdn.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/applepiesmoothie-15.jpg" alt="Spiced Apple Pie Smoothie (vegan, GF) - Sweet, creamy &amp; you know what they say...An apple pie smoothie a day keeps the doctor away!" width="546" height="800" data-pin-url="http://www.averiecooks.com/2012/02/spiced-apple-pie-smoothie.html" data-jpibfi-indexer="12" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="title"><a title="Blueberry Banana Recovery Smoothie" href="http://www.averiecooks.com/2011/10/blueberry-banana-recovery-smoothie.html" rel="bookmark">Blueberry Banana Recovery Smoothie</a> – Sweet, fruity, a little bit creamy, and very refreshing! A great post-workout smoothie!</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-11380 size-full" title="blueberrysmoothie-9" src="http://cdn.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/blueberrysmoothie-9.jpg" alt="Blueberry Banana Recovery Smoothie - Sweet, fruity, a little bit creamy, and very refreshing! A great post-workout smoothie!" width="555" height="800" data-pin-url="http://www.averiecooks.com/2011/10/blueberry-banana-recovery-smoothie.html" data-jpibfi-indexer="13" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="title"><a title="Coconut Cream Pie Smoothie" href="http://www.averiecooks.com/2012/08/coconut-cream-pie-smoothie.html" rel="bookmark">Coconut Cream Pie Smoothie</a> (vegan, GF) – Tastes like a slice of coconut cream pie! Creamy, smooth, and no sugar added!</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter" title="Coconut Cream Pie Smoothie (vegan, GF) - Tastes like a slice of coconut cream pie! Creamy, smooth, &amp; no sugar added!" src="http://cdn.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/coconutcreamsmoothiewords.jpg" alt="Coconut Cream Pie Smoothie (vegan, GF) - Tastes like a slice of coconut cream pie! Creamy, smooth, &amp; no sugar added!" width="598" height="800" data-pin-url="http://www.averiecooks.com/2012/08/coconut-cream-pie-smoothie.html" data-jpibfi-indexer="14" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="title"><a title="Skinny Caramel Frappuccino" href="http://www.averiecooks.com/2013/06/skinny-caramel-frappuccino.html" rel="bookmark">Skinny Caramel Frappuccino</a> – Move over Starbucks, this version only has 50 calories per serving! Thinks of all the money (and calories) you’ll save by making your own!</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-37939" title="Skinny Caramel Frappuccino - Only 50 Calories Per Serving - Recipe at averiecooks.com" src="http://cdn.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/caramelfrappuccino-19.jpg" alt="Skinny Caramel Frappuccino - Only 50 Calories Per Serving - Recipe at averiecooks.com" width="561" height="850" data-pin-url="http://www.averiecooks.com/2013/06/skinny-caramel-frappuccino.html" data-jpibfi-indexer="15" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="Berry Greens Vanilla Smoothie" href="http://www.averiecooks.com/2015/01/berry-greens-vanilla-smoothie.html">Berry Greens Vanilla Smoothie</a> – Healthy, easy, and tastes amazing!! You’d never guess it’s packed with greens and so good FOR you!</p>\r\n<img class="wp-image-53736 size-large aligncenter" src="http://cdn.averiecooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/berrygreenssmoothietext2-630x920.jpg" alt="Berry Greens Vanilla Smoothie - Healthy, easy, and tastes amazing!! You''d never guess it''s packed with greens and so good FOR you!!" width="630" height="920" data-pin-url="http://www.averiecooks.com/2015/01/berry-greens-vanilla-smoothie.html" data-jpibfi-indexer="16" />', '15 QUICK & EASY HEALTHY SMOOTHIE RECIPES', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '231-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-01-29 17:41:43', '2016-01-29 17:41:43', '', 231, 'http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/231-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(705, 5, '2016-01-29 17:48:07', '2016-01-29 17:48:07', '<p style="text-align: center;">Thinking of building in your range hood? Well its a good thing we have a huge selection of built in range hood ideas and inserts to choose from <strong><a href="http://directrangehoods.com/range-hood-inserts.html" target="_blank">HERE</a>.</strong> Check out these beautiful kitchens for ideas and inspiration on how to give your range hood area an elegant treatment.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1000226361.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-201" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1000226361.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg" alt="100022636.jpg.rendition.largest" width="600" height="500" /></a>Whoever thought that cooking pans would actually be an elegant addition above your kitchen range? Not only will it make it your pans easily accessible and cut down drying time, but it really will give a beautiful french countryside look to your kitchen space. The big white tiled arch also adds an openness to this kitchen which helps create a great environment to be in while cooking for long hours.\r\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1000332991.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-202" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1000332991.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg" alt="100033299.jpg.rendition.largest" width="600" height="500" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">This wall is an ideal location for your range hood. The arch acts a stylish overhang, creating a dramatic space for this vent hood, and its custom range hood cover.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1000774771.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-203" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1000774771.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg" alt="100077477.jpg.rendition.largest" width="600" height="600" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Beautiful woodwork surrounds this range hood to make it stand out in this monochromatic kitchen. The tile backsplash adds impact, and the stainless steel range hood blends quietly due to the use of a single color.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1001105571.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-204" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1001105571.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg" alt="100110557.jpg.rendition.largest" width="597" height="674" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">This checkered range hood design is one that is sure not to go unnoticed as it pulls the whole room together with the warm colors, and really creates a seamless feel connecting the range hood, backsplash, and countertop space beautifully.\r\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1001625281.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-205" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1001625281.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg" alt="100162528.jpg.rendition.largest" width="600" height="667" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">We love to find spaces that have function as well as tasteful design. This decorative tile subtly draws attention to the beautiful range while the distinguished border of  tile accentuates the arc over the entire area. The cabinetry over the range conceals the hood while also providing convenient storage.\r\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1001794961.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-206" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1001794961.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg" alt="100179496.jpg.rendition.largest" width="600" height="500" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Sometimes an eye catching arrangement just comes naturally. This English Manor house features an old style cooker that fits perfectly into this original fireplace, with an addition of the range hood inserted above. Now this is a fun way to maintain the homes feel of the past.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1002112261.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-207" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1002112261.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg" alt="100211226.jpg.rendition.largest" width="597" height="796" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"> Not only is this cooking area safe, with plenty of countertop space beside the range, but beautiful as the diamond - yellow and creme toned tile really pulls all of the colors of this kitchen space together beautifully.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/100229589-11.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-208" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/100229589-11.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg" alt="100229589-1.jpg.rendition.largest" width="594" height="793" /></a>Look at this kitchen, what is the first thing you notice? We notice the copper range hood that is displayed beautifully with the elegant tile backsplash and intricate arch design above the range. This kitchen space is airy, spacious, and has an elegance like no other due to each minor detail.  As a focal point, the range hood is a good place to introduce new colors or materials to a kitchen''s palette.\r\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1002374211.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-209" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1002374211.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg" alt="100237421.jpg.rendition.largest" width="593" height="791" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">This setup gives the range hood  area a stylish but practical nook. Cabinetry is great for storing everything from pots and pans to utensils and table linens. Open shelving on the other hand is a prime space for cookbooks, spices, and cooking oils. This kitchen range area includes all of these elements perfectly.<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1004523591.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-210" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1004523591.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg" alt="100452359.jpg.rendition.largest" width="596" height="795" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">This range hood area says "WALA" with the contrasting custom built cabinetry surrounding the appliances beautifully from the floor up to the ceiling. The open shelving on the side creates a useful space to store items without taking away from the appearance due to the decorative gray tile wall and medallion design making a stronger appearance underneath the range hood.<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1005750181.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-211" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1005750181.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg" alt="100575018.jpg.rendition.largest" width="600" height="600" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Brick shapes this range hood nook, complementing the kitchen''s exposed beam ceiling, wood island, wood flooring, and abundant natural light.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1006553631.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-212" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1006553631.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg" alt="100655363.jpg.rendition.largest" width="600" height="600" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">The typical range is surrounded by a range hood and cabinetry, but this kitchen''s designer took a different approach. Without vertical cabinets, countertops and kitchen space becomes more open. For a subtle emphasis, the range hood blends into the wall beautifully will the large wood trim. <a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1006701741.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-213" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1006701741.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg" alt="100670174.jpg.rendition.largest" width="598" height="665" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"> While this range is built into the cabinetry, it''s the brick wall behind the range that gets all the attention. Where a tile backsplash might normally cover the wall, this kitchen has a wood-burning pizza oven installed IN THE WALL. Seriously how cool is this?  This distinctive feature is a great option for entertaining or preparing feasts for your family to enjoy.<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1009472371.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-214" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1009472371.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg" alt="100947237.jpg.rendition.largest" width="604" height="671" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">This space boasts soft cottage colors and a limestone range area. The backsplash is exceptionally detailed with multiple types of tile, including three hand-painted scenic tiles, blending to create the kitchen''s own work of art. The vintage-style white range complements the cottage decor while blending with the creamy cabinetry to keep attention focused on the tiling and not on the range hood above. <a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1011924851.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-215" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1011924851.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg" alt="101192485.jpg.rendition.largest" width="600" height="500" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Don''t be afraid to mix the traditional style of a range with the modern look of stainless steel. Instead of being hidden, this hood actually extends the length of the entire space. It serves as a visual bridge between the refrigerator and the freezer. The cool feel and clean lines of the metal contrast with the warm cabinetry while complementing the simple design.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1012951041.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-216" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1012951041.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg" alt="101295104.jpg.rendition.largest" width="600" height="500" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Texture is a contemporary way to spice up kitchen decor. The stone outline of this range hood area adds a rough and natural component to the smooth surfaces of the island, cabinets, and countertops. While the stone gives emphasis to the range nook, the kitchen''s earth tones harmonize with the natural elements to keep the space united and refreshing. <a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1012957841.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-217" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1012957841.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg" alt="101295784.jpg.rendition.largest" width="600" height="500" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Try customizing your range to your kitchen -- or your kitchen to your range! The focal point of this kitchen is its uncommon white range with gold knobs and trim. The white subway backsplash accentuates the appliances by reflecting  gorgeous bright light. Built-in display cabinets also frame the range nook and imitate its arched style. The range hood insert is a secret in this kitchen with all of the power functionality remaining and less emphasis on the visual appeal.<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/TDH7230741.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-218" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/TDH7230741.jpg.rendition.largest1.jpg" alt="TDH723074.jpg.rendition.largest" width="597" height="664" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">This is truly a built-in range area: The range, hood, cabinetry, and side shelving are entirely built into the wall. The wide arch and beautiful mood lighting smooths the transition of this kitchen space while making a statement that is sure to be noticed. This separates the cooking area from the social space  in such a fun way.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Hopefully this gave you some unique ideas of ways to enhance the look of your kitchen range hood space. Let us know which one is your favorite in the comments box below.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Don''t forget to subscribe for new and fresh kitchen design ideas, recipes, kitchen tips and more!</p>', 'Beautiful Built In Range Hood Ideas', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '200-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-01-29 17:48:07', '2016-01-29 17:48:07', '', 200, 'http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/200-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(706, 5, '2016-01-29 18:21:44', '2016-01-29 18:21:44', '<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/no-bake-cake-batter-truffles-11.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-88 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/no-bake-cake-batter-truffles-11.jpg" alt="no bake cake batter truffles 1" width="1000" height="661" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nLooking for a quick and easy dessert recipe that is both festive and delicious? Do you love truffles as much as we do? Well look no further, because we have the perfect recipe for you, these No Bake - Cake Batter Truffles will leave your mouth watering and your guests coming back for more. You can easily make these in as little as 15-25 minutes with very little ingredients and no oven necessary! This is the perfect dessert to make for your kids, bring to a party, take into work, or best yet - to treat yourself with. After all, you deserve a little sweet treat every now and then!<!--more-->\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/no-bake-cake-batter-truffles-11.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-91 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/unnamed-3-e14395732212131.jpg" alt="unnamed-3" width="1000" height="563" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/unnamed-e14395732011221.jpg"><img class=" wp-image-89 size-full aligncenter" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/unnamed-e14395732011221.jpg" alt="unnamed" width="1000" height="563" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/unnamed-1-e14395732129461.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-90 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/unnamed-1-e14395732129461.jpg" alt="unnamed-1" width="1000" height="563" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/unnamed-4-e14395732315111.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-92 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/unnamed-4-e14395732315111.jpg" alt="unnamed-4" width="1000" height="563" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p id="zlrecipe-ingredients" class="h-4 strong"><strong>Ingredients</strong></p>\r\n<p class="h-4 strong"><strong><span class="bold">For the Truffles:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul id="zlrecipe-ingredients-list">\r\n	<li id="zlrecipe-ingredient-1" class="ingredient">1-1/2 c. flour</li>\r\n	<li id="zlrecipe-ingredient-2" class="ingredient">1 c. yellow cake mix</li>\r\n	<li id="zlrecipe-ingredient-3" class="ingredient">1/2 c. unsalted <span id="IL_AD11" class="IL_AD">butter</span>, softened</li>\r\n	<li id="zlrecipe-ingredient-4" class="ingredient">1/2 c. white sugar</li>\r\n	<li id="zlrecipe-ingredient-5" class="ingredient">1 tsp. vanilla</li>\r\n	<li id="zlrecipe-ingredient-6" class="ingredient">1/8 tsp. salt</li>\r\n	<li id="zlrecipe-ingredient-7" class="ingredient">3-4 tbsp. milk</li>\r\n	<li id="zlrecipe-ingredient-8" class="ingredient">2 tbsp. sprinkles</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><span class="bold">For the Coating:</span></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>16 oz. (8 squares) almond bark or vanilla flavored coating</li>\r\n	<li id="zlrecipe-ingredient-11" class="ingredient">Sprinkles</li>\r\n	<li id="zlrecipe-ingredient-12" class="ingredient">Pop sticks (for dipping)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p id="zlrecipe-instructions" class="h-4 strong"><strong>Instructions</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol id="zlrecipe-instructions-list" class="instructions">\r\n	<li id="zlrecipe-instruction-0" class="instruction">For the truffles: Beat together butter and sugar using an electric mixer until combined. Add cake mix, flour, salt, and vanilla and mix thoroughly. Add 3–4 tbsp. of milk (I used 3) if needed to make a dough consistency. Mix in sprinkles by hand.</li>\r\n	<li id="zlrecipe-instruction-1" class="instruction"><span id="IL_AD1" class="IL_AD">Roll</span> dough into one-inch balls and place on parchment or wax paper on a cookie sheet. Chill balls in the <span id="IL_AD6" class="IL_AD">refrigerator</span> for 15 minutes to firm up.</li>\r\n	<li id="zlrecipe-instruction-2" class="instruction">For the coating: While dough balls are chilling, melt almond bark in the microwave in 30 second intervals until melted. Stir between intervals.</li>\r\n	<li id="zlrecipe-instruction-3" class="instruction">Using a pop stick, dip truffles into melted almond bark and gently twirl around to <span id="IL_AD12" class="IL_AD">remove</span>excess coating. Place truffle back on cookie sheet and top with sprinkles. Repeat with remaining balls until finished.</li>\r\n	<li id="zlrecipe-instruction-4" class="instruction">Chill truffles in the refrigerator until ready to serve.</li>\r\n	<li id="zlrecipe-instruction-5" class="instruction">Makes approximately <strong>24–30 truffles.</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RSOPdwxASLw&feature=youtu.be\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">We hope that you have enjoyed this Recipe! Let us know in the comments box below what you would like us to make next! Enjoy!</p>', 'No Bake - Cake Batter Truffles', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '87-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-01-29 18:21:44', '2016-01-29 18:21:44', '', 87, 'http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/87-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
