(733, 5, '2016-03-02 00:22:13', '2016-03-02 00:22:13', '<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Holiday-Dessert-Tools.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-639 size-large" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Holiday-Dessert-Tools-1024x678.jpg" alt="Tools for Holiday Desserts" width="1024" height="678" /></a>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">The Holidays are here and that means it''s baking Season!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Need a good neighbor gift? A Killer Dessert Recipe for a the Annual Christmas Family Party? Or are you just in the Christmas spirit and craving a holiday treat for you and your loved ones?</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Well you are in the right place! We have rounded up all of our favorites, and we are excited to share them with you! Enjoy!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">1. <a href="http://thefoodcharlatan.com/2014/12/19/candy-cane-brownie-trifle/" target="_blank">Candy Cane Brownie Trifle -The Food Charlatan</a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_640" align="aligncenter" width="648"]<a href="http://thefoodcharlatan.com/2014/12/19/candy-cane-brownie-trifle/" target="_blank" rel="attachment wp-att-640"><img class="wp-image-640 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/3a366f1015c947dfec02756839e9c3cf-e1450722688711.jpg" alt="Candy Cane Brownie Trifle" width="648" height="936" /></a> Courtesy of The Food Charlatan[/caption]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">2.<a href="http://www.somethingswanky.com/better-than-christmas-poke-cake/">Better Than Christmas Poke Cake - Something Swanky</a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n[caption id="" align="aligncenter" width="600"]<a href="http://www.somethingswanky.com/better-than-christmas-poke-cake/" target="_blank"><img src="http://i2.wp.com/www.somethingswanky.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/DSC_2096-edited-watermarked.png?resize=600%2C896" alt="Better than Christmas Poke Cake" width="600" height="896" /></a> Courtesy of Something Swanky[/caption]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">3.<a href="http://foodfolksandfun.net/2015/12/peppermint-bark-brownies/" target="_blank">Peppermint Bark Brownies - Food, Folks, and Fun</a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n[caption id="" align="aligncenter" width="733"]<a href="http://foodfolksandfun.net/2015/12/peppermint-bark-brownies/"><img class="" src="http://foodfolksandfun.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Peppermint-Bark-Brownies.jpg" alt="Peppermint Bark Brownies" width="733" height="1100" /></a> Courtesy of Food, Folks, and Fun[/caption]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">4<a href="http://www.delish.com/cooking/recipe-ideas/recipes/a45137/hot-chocolate-french-silk-pie-recipe/" target="_blank">.Hot Chocolate French Silk Pie - Delish</a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n[caption id="" align="aligncenter" width="980"]<a href="http://www.delish.com/cooking/recipe-ideas/recipes/a45137/hot-chocolate-french-silk-pie-recipe/"><img class="" src="http://del.h-cdn.co/assets/15/50/980x490/landscape-1449686746-hot-chocolate-french-silk-pie-11-1.jpg" alt="Hot Chocolate French Silk Pie" width="980" height="490" /></a> Courtesy of Delish[/caption]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">5.<a href="http://www.portuguesegirlcooks.com/2012/12/1310/#sthash.5Xck6Qbf.qjtu" target="_blank">Chocolate-Espresso Buche de Noel - Portuguese Girl Cooks</a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n[caption id="" align="aligncenter" width="600"]<a href="http://www.portuguesegirlcooks.com/2012/12/1310/#sthash.5Xck6Qbf.qjtu"><img class="" src="http://www.portuguesegirlcooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/Bouche-Noel-1.jpg" alt="Chocolate-Espresso Buche de Noel" width="600" height="900" /></a> Courtesy of Portuguese Girl Cooks[/caption]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">6<a href="http://Jamie''s Mum''s gorgeous chocolate pudding" target="_blank">.Jamie''s Mum''s Gorgeous Chocolate Pudding - Jamie Oliver</a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n[caption id="" align="aligncenter" width="767"]<a href="http://www.jamieoliver.com/recipes/chocolate-recipes/jamie-s-mum-s-gorgeous-chocolate-pudding/#xhuFKjIX87bqPO5H.97"><img class="" src="https://jamieoliverprod.s3.amazonaws.com/recipe-database/oldImages/recipe_single/720_1_1436803588.jpg" alt="Chocolate Pudding - Christmas Dessert" width="767" height="1025" /></a> Courtesy of Jamie Oliver[/caption]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">7. <a href="http://boysahoy.com/peppermint-chocolate-marshmallow-cookies-2/" target="_blank">Peppermint Chocolate Marshmallow Cookies - Boys Ahoy</a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n[caption id="" align="aligncenter" width="427"]<a href="http://boysahoy.com/peppermint-chocolate-marshmallow-cookies-2/"><img class="" src="http://sweettreatsmore.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/IMG_9653.jpg" alt="Peppermint Chocolate Marshmallow Cookies - Christmas Desserts" width="427" height="640" /></a> Courtesy of Boys Ahoy[/caption]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">8.<a href="http://skinnynotskinny.com/peppermint-oreo-cookie-brownies/" target="_blank">Peppermint Oreo Cookie Brownies - Skinny Not Skinny</a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n[caption id="" align="aligncenter" width="550"]<a href="http://skinnynotskinny.com/peppermint-oreo-cookie-brownies/"><img class="" src="http://skinnynotskinny.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/peppbrownies.jpg" alt="Peppermint Oreo Cookie Brownies - Christmas Desserts" width="550" height="367" /></a> Courtesy of Skinny Not Skinny[/caption]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">9. <a href="http://www.swankyrecipes.com/peppermint-eggnog-milkshake.html" target="_blank">Peppermint Eggnog Milkshake - Swanky Recipes</a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n[caption id="" align="aligncenter" width="427"]<a href="http://www.swankyrecipes.com/peppermint-eggnog-milkshake.html"><img class="" src="http://cdn.swankyrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Peppermint-Eggnog-Milkshake.jpg" alt="Peppermint Eggnog Milkshake - Holiday Desserts" width="427" height="640" /></a> Courtesy of Swanky Recipes[/caption]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">10.<a href="http://lifescoops.blogspot.com/2013/11/crepe-cake-with-blackberry-schnapps.html" target="_blank"> Blackberry Crepe Cake - Life Scoops</a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n[caption id="" align="aligncenter" width="1062"]<a href="http://lifescoops.blogspot.com/2013/11/crepe-cake-with-blackberry-schnapps.html"><img class="" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-7NQ3eST3X6c/Un2jaiG6XII/AAAAAAAALoc/l4Emvoedcuo/s1600/DSC_0656+with+title.jpg" alt="Blackberry Chocolate Mousse Cake - holiday desserts" width="1062" height="1600" /></a> Courtesy of Life Scoops[/caption]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">We Hope you are having a Happy Holiday Season. Stay warm, and remember that calories don''t count on Christmas!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">If you love what you see, SUBSCRIBE to be up to date with Recipes, Design Inspiration, and More!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Happy Holidays!</p>', '10 Best Holiday Desserts', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '638-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-02 00:22:13', '2016-03-02 00:22:13', '', 638, 'http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/638-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
