"1151"]<a class="stainless_steel_range_hood_proline_range_hoods_" href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/stainless_steel_range_hood.jpg" target="_blank" rel="http://www.prolinerangehoods.com/index.php?main_page=product_info&amp;cPath=32_48&amp;products_id=345"><img class="stainless_steel_range_hood_proline_range_hoods_ wp-image-743" title="stainless_steel_range_hood_proline_range_hoods_" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/stainless_steel_range_hood.jpg" alt="kitchen unique stainless_steel_range_hood_unique_kitchen" width="1151" height="758" /></a> <a href="http://www.prolinerangehoods.com/index.php?main_page=product_info&amp;cPath=32_48&amp;products_id=345" target="_blank">Range Hood: Proline PLFW 750 Wall Mount Range Hood</a>[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_746" align="aligncenter" width="1147"]<a class="stainless_steel_range_hood_proline_range_hoods_PLFW_750" href="http://www.prolinerangehoods.com/index.php?main_page=product_info&amp;cPath=32_48&amp;products_id=333" rel="stainless_steel_range_hood_proline_range_hoods_PLFW_750"><img class="wp-image-746" title="stainless_steel_range_hoods_proline_range_hoods_PLFW_750" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/proline_range_hood.jpg" alt="kitchen unique stainless_steel_proline_range_hoods_PLFW_750" width="1147" height="756" /></a> <a href="http://stainless_steel_range_hood_proline_range_hoods" target="_blank">Range Hood: Proline PLFW 750</a>[/caption]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h3> Its all about the <b>Details, Details, Details...</b></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nHave you ever heard the quote:\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">"When it comes to design modesty is great,</h2>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">and quietness is nice, but letting your</h2>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">imagination run free is always more fun." <span class="_58cl"><a class="_58cn" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/kitcheninspiration?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1049630345073624" data-ft="{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;*N&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:104}">‪</a> </span></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span class="_58cl">Your kitchen should be your absolute favorite room in your home, not just a place to cook, but more so, a place where you feel free to be be yourself, create, and feel inspired. Why be so serious when it comes to design? Our advice – be original and make your kitchen feel like nobody but you could own it! These rooms shown below are both beautiful, and unique kitchen spaces. We have to believe that a kitchen can say a lot about the person who owns it. Taking a kitchen from bland to grand is all in the details. No need to get too crazy and blow your money on the most custom and  intricate details, but you will be amazed with what elements you will be able to  find that are actually just as affordable. Here are some of our favorite stand out details to acknowledge when designing your own Kitchen:</span>\r\n\r\n<strong>The Floor:</strong>\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_749" align="aligncenter" width="1147"]<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/kitchen_unique_kitchen_floor-1.png" rel="mediterranean_floor_tile_kitchen_unique_proline_kitchen_blog"><img class="wp-image-749" title="mediterranean_floor_tile_kitchen_unique_proline_kitchen_blog" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/kitchen_unique_kitchen_floor-1.png" alt="kitchen unique mediterranean_floor_tile_kitchen_unique_proline_kitchen_blog" width="1147" height="909" /></a> Beautiful Black and White Mediterranean Floor Tile, Such a Dream.[/caption]\r\n\r\n<strong>The Hardware:</strong>\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_751" align="aligncenter" width="1147"]<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/kitchen_unique_kitchen_hardware_proline_kitchen_blog-1.png" rel="kitchen_unique_kitchen_hardware_proline_kitchen_blog"><img class="kitchen_unique_kitchen_hardware_proline_kitchen_blog wp-image-751 size-full" title="kitchen_unique_kitchen_hardware_proline_kitchen_blog" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/kitchen_unique_kitchen_hardware_proline_kitchen_blog-1.png" alt="kitchen unique_kitchen_hardware_proline_kitchen_blog" width="1147" height="1263" /></a> Finding Unique Kitchen Hardware is Everything.[/caption]\r\n\r\n<strong>The Lighting:</strong>\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_752" align="aligncenter" width="1147"]<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/kitchen-unique-kitchen_lighting_proline_kitchen_blog.png" rel="kitchen unique kitchen_lighting_proline_kitchen_blog"><img class="kitchen unique kitchen_lighting_proline_kitchen_blog wp-image-752 size-full" title="kitchen unique kitchen_lighting_proline_kitchen_blog" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/kitchen-unique-kitchen_lighting_proline_kitchen_blog-e1457631060196.png" alt="kitchen unique kitchen_lighting_proline_kitchen_blog" width="1147" height="835" /></a> A dazzling pendant light is the focal point in this Unique Kitchen.[/caption]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h3> Give it some Natural Flair &amp; Personality.</h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nMaking a kitchen unique is all about making it feel like its yours. Are you a big baker &amp; entertainer who would  enjoy nothing more in a kitchen space than for it to be bright and cheerful just like you? Or are you a person with a passion for world travel who enjoys finding unique imported custom pieces  from around the world? You can bring all of these great personality traits  and really personalize a room with all of the things that you love. You only have one life to live, so if you ask us, it makes perfect sense to invest some heartfelt thought and consideration into the room where you will spend the most time, the kitchen.  What would give your kitchen that extra oomph that you desire? .. Here are some of our favorite design elements to really add some extra personality to your Kitchen Space:\r\n\r\n<strong>Wall Colors &amp; Textures:</strong>\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_792" align="aligncenter" width="1164"]<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Exposed-brick-walls-and-lighting-create-a-distinct-modern-industrial-style-in-the-kitchen.jpg" rel="attachment wp-att-792"><img class="wp-image-792" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Exposed-brick-walls-and-lighting-create-a-distinct-modern-industrial-style-in-the-kitchen-682x1024.jpg" alt="kitchen unique" width="1164" height="1748" /></a> The exposed brick walls give this kitchen an industrial feel.[/caption]\r\n\r\n<strong>Furniture:</strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/unique-kitchen-barstools.png" rel="attachment wp-att-794"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-794 " src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/unique-kitchen-barstools-815x1024.png" alt="kitchen unique" width="1148" height="1439" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Decor:</strong>\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_795" align="aligncenter" width="1142"]<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/kitchen-unique-blue-and-white-kitchen-decor.png" rel="attachment wp-att-795"><img class="wp-image-795 " src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/kitchen-unique-blue-and-white-kitchen-decor-1024x777.png" alt="kitchen unique" width="1142" height="867" /></a> Beautiful Porcelain, faux flowers, and some blue glass, really take this kitchen up a notch.[/caption]\r\n\r\n<strong>Rugs:</strong>\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_796" align="aligncenter" width="1138"]<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/kitchen-unique-kitchen-rug.png" rel="attachment wp-att-796"><img class="wp-image-796" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/kitchen-unique-kitchen-rug-1024x727.png" alt="kitchen unique" width="1138" height="811" /></a> This rug pulls all of the design elements and color together beautifully.[/caption]\r\n\r\n<strong>Art:</strong>\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_797" align="aligncenter" width="1111"]<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/kitchen-unique-kitchen-wall-art.png" rel="attachment wp-att-797"><img class="wp-image-797 " src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/kitchen-unique-kitchen-wall-art-1024x721.png" alt="kitchen unique" width="1111" height="833" /></a> Above All Have Fun, a lesson to be learned in both design, and life.[/caption]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Tip:</strong> Before designing your Kitchen, it''s a great idea to make an inspiration board of different color schemes, furniture peices, appliance pictures, and whatever else you are feeling to get all of your ideas in one place and help give you get a better feel for your new dream Kitchen Space.\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_799" align="aligncenter" width="1117"]<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/kitchen-unique-kitchen-design-inspiration.jpg" rel="attachment wp-att-799"><img class="wp-image-799" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/kitchen-unique-kitchen-design-inspiration-1024x681.jpg" alt="kitchen unique" width="1117" height="759" /></a> Make the design process fun, and give yourself an idea of the final project before it''s finished.[/caption]\r\n\r\nMaking a kitchen unique is all in the details. From the Walls, to the the floors, to every design element. We hope you feel a little more prepared to start your own kitchen remodeling process, and we are here to help. At Proline we truly believe that making your kitchen unique starts with the appliances, and finding a top quality and beautiful Range Hood is a great place to start. If you are looking into giving your kitchen a makeover, moving, or know somebody who is, we have a great team of people that would love to help make your dream Kitchen come to life. Visit our website to get a peak at our unique and affordable range hood selection: <a href="http://www.prolinerangehoods.com">www.prolinerangehoods.com</a>.\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Thank you for stopping by, and we hope to see you around! Make sure to subscribe to our blog to stay updated on the latest and greatest in kitchen design.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">-Your Friends At Proline</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'What Makes a Kitchen Unique?', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '739-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-28 21:32:41', '2016-03-28 21:32:41', '', 739, 'http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/739-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
