(820, 1, '2016-04-19 22:25:17', '2016-04-19 22:25:17', '<h1 style="text-align: center;">8 Backsplash Ideas To Show Off Your Cooking Space</h1>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Exactly what is it that makes a cooking space more enjoyable, and beautiful? We were surprised to find how much a backsplash can enhance the look of a kitchen, and the significant difference this makes when it comes to showing off your beautiful range hood and kitchen appliances. Let''s face it, when you’re picking your kitchen backsplash, it’s mostly about showing off your cooking zone where you get to be the chef. How do you showcase your personal style? You’re probably wondering what to put on that empty wall above your stove, or possibly just looking for some kitchen inspiration? Whether you prefer a modern seamless design, accent wall, or a metal accent piece, the right backsplash can make all the difference.  Kitchen design lovers, this one is for you. So, sit back, and enjoy as we share our favorite 10 backsplash ideas to show off your cooking space.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Herringbone Tile</h2>\r\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/herringbone_tile_backsplash_ideas.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-812 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/herringbone_tile_backsplash_ideas.jpg" alt="backsplash herringbone_tile_backsplash_ideas" width="1000" height="674" /></a>\r\n<h2>Subway Tile</h2>\r\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/gray_blue_subway_tile_backsplash_white_kitchen.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-813 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/gray_blue_subway_tile_backsplash_white_kitchen.jpg" alt="backsplash gray_blue_subway_tile_backsplash_white_kitchen" width="1000" height="674" /></a>\r\n<h2>Mosaic Tile</h2>\r\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/blue_mosaic_tile_kitchen_backsplash_range_hood_cover_white_kitchen.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-814 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/blue_mosaic_tile_kitchen_backsplash_range_hood_cover_white_kitchen.jpg" alt="backsplash blue_mosaic_tile_kitchen_backsplash_range_hood_cover_white_kitchen" width="1000" height="674" /></a>\r\n<h2>Brick</h2>\r\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/brick_backsplash_blue_kitchen_range_hood_insert.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-815 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/brick_backsplash_blue_kitchen_range_hood_insert.jpg" alt="backsplash brick_backsplash_blue_kitchen_range_hood_insert" width="1000" height="674" /></a>\r\n<h2>Stainless Steel</h2>\r\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/stainless_steel_backsplash_kitchen_ideas.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-816 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/stainless_steel_backsplash_kitchen_ideas.jpg" alt="backsplash stainless_steel_backsplash_kitchen_ideas" width="1000" height="674" /></a>\r\n<h2>Accent Wall</h2>\r\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/accent_wall_kitchen_backsplash_white_kitchen_undercabinet_range_hood_white_kitchen.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-819 aligncenter" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/accent_wall_kitchen_backsplash_white_kitchen_undercabinet_range_hood_white_kitchen.jpg" alt="backsplash accent_wall_kitchen_backsplash_white_kitchen_undercabinet_range_hood_white_kitchen" width="1000" height="674" /></a>\r\n<h2>Natural Stone</h2>\r\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/natural_stone_backsplash_ideas_luxury_kitchen_custom_range_hood_cover.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-818 aligncenter" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/natural_stone_backsplash_ideas_luxury_kitchen_custom_range_hood_cover.jpg" alt="backsplash natural_stone_backsplash_ideas_luxury_kitchen_custom_range_hood_cover" width="1000" height="674" /></a>\r\n<h2>Seamless Design</h2>\r\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/seamless_kitchen_backsplash_ideas.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-817 size-full" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/seamless_kitchen_backsplash_ideas.jpg" alt="backsplash seamless_kitchen_backsplash_ideas" width="1000" height="674" /></a>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Thanks for stopping by our Kitchen blog, let us know what your favorites are in the comments box below.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Don''t forget to subscribe and join the fun as we celebrate beautiful kitchens, share delicious recipes, kitchen tips and more.</p>', '8 Backsplash Ideas To Show Off Your Cooking Space', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '809-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-04-19 22:25:17', '2016-04-19 22:25:17', '', 809, 'http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/809-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(823, 1, '2016-05-10 19:39:54', '2016-05-10 19:39:54', '<h1 style="text-align: center;">Range Hoods: The Secret Addition For A Beautiful Kitchen</h1>\r\nVent hoods to some, may seem like they are not the most "glamorous" part of kitchen design.  Many do not even understand the importance or benefits of having a range hood in their own homes regardless of the safety codes and regulations that have been made in some states. However, now interior designers and house professionals are considering  range hoods to be a crucial investment for any kitchen space as they are considering these appliances to be not only the powerful force behind having fresh clean air, but also a really beautiful showpiece in the kitchen.\r\n<h2>Range Hoods are The Statement Pieces In Any Kitchen</h2>\r\nWe have shared some of our favorite kitchen spaces where the range hood truly makes the space more beautiful. Designers are calling range hoods the "trophy," "the statement piece," and the "superstar of the kitchen," and we couldn''t agree more.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/range-hoods-beautiful-kichen-1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-831" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/range-hoods-beautiful-kichen-1.jpg" alt="stainless steel range hoods blue tile backsplash" width="800" height="671" /></a>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">( <a href="http://www.houzz.com/pro/mckinleyarchitects">Image Credit: MckinLey Architects </a>)</p>\r\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/white_traditional_kitchen_gray_blue_accents_custom-range-hoods-_cover_insert_hood-copy.png"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-834" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/white_traditional_kitchen_gray_blue_accents_custom-range-hoods-_cover_insert_hood-copy-1024x674.png" alt="white_traditional_kitchen_gray_blue_accents_custom range hoods _cover_insert_hood copy" width="800" height="527" /></a>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">(<a href="http://www.homebunch.com/harbor-springs-lake-cottage/"> Image Credit: Home Bunch</a> )</p>\r\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/range-hoods-stainless-steel-proline-36-inch-vent-hood.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-835" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/range-hoods-stainless-steel-proline-36-inch-vent-hood.jpg" alt="range hoods stainless-steel-proline-36-inch-vent-hood" width="800" height="601" /></a>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">(<a href="http://www.hgtv.com/design/rooms/kitchens"> Image Credit: BHG</a>  )</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/stainless-steel-range-hoods.jpg"><img class="alignnone wp-image-832" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/stainless-steel-range-hoods.jpg" alt="stainless-steel- range hoods" width="800" height="607" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">(<a href="http://remodeling.sfgate.com/photos/mediterranean/kitchen/backsplash-material--stone-slab"> Image Credit: SF Gate </a>)</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/white_kitchen_yellow_bar_stools_wall_mount_-range-hoods-.png"><img class="alignnone wp-image-833" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/white_kitchen_yellow_bar_stools_wall_mount_-range-hoods-.png" alt="stainless-steel- range hoods -yellow-barstools-white-kitchen" width="800" height="800" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">( <a href="http://www.houzz.com/pro/alysdesign/alys-design">Image Credit:  Alys Design</a> )</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Range Hoods Provide Both Beauty and Function</h2>\r\nThere is nothing worse than an appliance that comes with no aesthetics or appeal, made merely to get the job done, yet completely unattractive. A range hood should be both functional and and beautiful, and below we have shared some of our favorite customer kitchens featuring some of our Proline hoods that we believe to be exactly this –both appealing &amp; powerful.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_836" align="aligncenter" width="800"]<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/red_kitchen_stainless_steel_-range-hoods-_30_inch_wall_hood_contemporary_kitchen_appliances_pendant_lighting_darkwood_cabinets.jpg"><img class="wp-image-836" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/red_kitchen_stainless_steel_-range-hoods-_30_inch_wall_hood_contemporary_kitchen_appliances_pendant_lighting_darkwood_cabinets-1024x682.jpg" alt="red_kitchen_stainless_steel_ range hoods _30_inch_wall_hood_contemporary_kitchen_appliances_pendant_lighting_darkwood_cabinets" width="800" height="533" /></a> Real Customer Kitchen Featuring the <a href="http://www.prolinerangehoods.com/index.php?main_page=product_info&amp;cPath=31_41&amp;products_id=338">Proline PLFW 750 Stainless Steel Wall Range Hood</a>  Interior Design by: <a href="http://falkenreynolds.com/">Chad Falkenberg Falken Reynolds</a>[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_838" align="aligncenter" width="800"]<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/proline-glass-island-range-hoods-proline-customer-white-kitchen.jpg"><img class="wp-image-838" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/proline-glass-island-range-hoods-proline-customer-white-kitchen.jpg" alt="proline-glass-island- range hoods - proline - customer-white-kitchen" width="800" height="600" /></a> Real Customer Kitchen Featuring the <a href="http://www.prolinerangehoods.com/index.php?main_page=product_info&amp;cPath=31_40&amp;products_id=290">Proline PLFI 544 Stainless Island Mount Range Hood</a>[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_839" align="aligncenter" width="800"]<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/stainless-steel-island-range-hoods-dark-wood-kitchen-proline-range-hoods.jpg"><img class="wp-image-839" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/stainless-steel-island-range-hoods-dark-wood-kitchen-proline-range-hoods-1024x761.jpg" alt="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/stainless-steel-island-range-hoods-dark-wood-kitchen-proline-range-hoods.jpg" width="800" height="594" /></a> Real Customer Kitchen Featuring the <a href="http://www.prolinerangehoods.com/index.php?main_page=product_info&amp;cPath=31_42&amp;products_id=459">Proline PROVI Stainless Steel Island Mount Range Hood</a>[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_840" align="aligncenter" width="800"]<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/stainless-steel-wall-mount-range-hoods-PLFW520-Proline.jpg"><img class="wp-image-840" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/stainless-steel-wall-mount-range-hoods-PLFW520-Proline-1024x761.jpg" alt="stainless-steel-wall-mount-range hoods PLFW520-Proline" width="800" height="594" /></a> Real Customer Kitchen Featuring the <a href="http://stainless-steel-wall-mount-range hoods PLFW520-Proline">Proline PLFW 520 Stainless Steel Wall Mount Range Hood.</a>[/caption]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Stainless Steel: The Design Trend That''s Here to Stay</h2>\r\nIt official, stainless steel appliances are holding firm. Don’t worry that your stainless fridge is going to be a heavy outdated monster in a few years, or that your range hood needs a custom cover to match your cabinets, because a whopping 75 percent of those who surveyed in a recent <a href="http://www.houzz.com">Houzz</a> study were going with stainless for their new appliances in their updated kitchens. (White came in at 10 percent and black at 8 percent.) This is a solid design trend, that will remain to stay sophisticated &amp; beautiful for years to come.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/stainless-steel-range-hoods-and-appliances.jpeg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-841" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/stainless-steel-range-hoods-and-appliances-1024x683.jpeg" alt="stainless-steel range hoods-and-appliances" width="800" height="533" /></a>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">( <a href="http://www.interiorcharm.com/kitchen/white-kitchens/">Image Credit:  Interior Charm </a>)</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Let us know which kitchen is your favorite in the comments section below.  Don''t forget to subscribe for the best kitchen inspiration, tips, recipes, and more.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">We would love for you to join us as we celebrate everything fun in the kitchen and celebrate home improvement!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">We hope you''ve found this post to be helpful. A range hood, does not need to be just a hood fan..</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Pick the right hood for your kitchen, and it will surely add that major design punch and powerful function that you have been wanting.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">If you are looking into purchasing a range hood and don''t even know where to begin, don''t even worry. Because at Proline Range Hoods we''ve got your back!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Take a peak of our top quality range hood selection over on our site : <a href="http://www.prolinerangehoods.com">www.prolinerangehoods.com</a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Wishing you a splendid Monday and a great rest of your week!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">-Your Friends At Proline</p>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Range Hoods: The Secret Addition For A Beautiful Kitchen', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'range-hoods-making-kitchens-beautiful', '', '', '2016-07-06 19:59:34', '2016-07-06 19:59:34', '', 0, 'http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/?p=823', 0, 'post', '', 0),
