"621" /></a>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">(<a href="http://www.homebunch.com/harbor-springs-lake-cottage/"> Image Credit: Home Bunch</a> )</p>\r\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/range-hoods-stainless-steel-proline-36-inch-vent-hood.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-835 " src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/range-hoods-stainless-steel-proline-36-inch-vent-hood.jpg" alt="range hoods stainless-steel-proline-36-inch-vent-hood" width="938" height="718" /></a>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">(<a href="http://www.hgtv.com/design/rooms/kitchens"> Image Credit: BHG</a>  )</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/stainless-steel-range-hoods.jpg"><img class="alignnone wp-image-832 " src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/stainless-steel-range-hoods.jpg" alt="stainless-steel- range hoods" width="955" height="725" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">(<a href="http://remodeling.sfgate.com/photos/mediterranean/kitchen/backsplash-material--stone-slab"> Image Credit: SF Gate </a>)</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/white_kitchen_yellow_bar_stools_wall_mount_-range-hoods-.png"><img class="alignnone wp-image-833 " src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/white_kitchen_yellow_bar_stools_wall_mount_-range-hoods-.png" alt="stainless-steel- range hoods -yellow-barstools-white-kitchen" width="935" height="942" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">( Image Credit: )</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Range Hoods Provide Both Beauty and Function</h2>\r\nThere is nothing worse than an appliance that comes with no aesthetics or appeal, made merely to get the job done, yet completely unattractive. A range hood should be both functional and and beautiful, and below we have shared some of our favorite customer kitchens featuring some 