.jpg" alt="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/stainless-steel-island-range-hoods-dark-wood-kitchen-proline-range-hoods.jpg" width="959" height="716" /></a> Featuring the <a href="http://www.prolinerangehoods.com/index.php?main_page=product_info&amp;cPath=31_42&amp;products_id=459">Proline PROVI Stainless Steel Island Mount Range Hood</a>[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_840" align="aligncenter" width="954"]<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/stainless-steel-wall-mount-range-hoods-PLFW520-Proline.jpg"><img class="wp-image-840 " src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/stainless-steel-wall-mount-range-hoods-PLFW520-Proline-1024x761.jpg" alt="stainless-steel-wall-mount-range hoods PLFW520-Proline" width="954" height="715" /></a> Featuring the <a href="http://stainless-steel-wall-mount-range hoods PLFW520-Proline">Proline PLFW 520 Stainless Steel Wall Mount Range Hood.</a>[/caption]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Stainless Steel: The Design Trend That''s Here to Stay</h2>\r\nIt official, stainless steel appliances are holding firm. Don’t worry that your stainless fridge is going to be a heavy outdated monster in a few years, or that your range hood needs a custom cover to match your cabinets, because a whopping 75 percent of those who surveyed in a recent <a href="http://www.houzz.com">Houzz</a> study were going with stainless for their new appliances in their updated kitchens. (White came in at 10 percent and black at 8 percent.) This is a solid design trend, that will remain to stay sophisticated &amp; beautiful for years to come.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/stainless-steel-range-hoods-and-appliances.jpeg"><img class=" wp-image-841 aligncenter" src="http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/stainless-steel-range-hoods-and-appliances-1024x683.jpeg" alt="stainless-steel range hoods-and-appliances" width="960" height="636" /></a>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">( Image Credit: )</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Let us know which kitchen is your favorite in the comments section below.  Don''t forget to subscribe for the best kitchen inspiration, tips, recipes, and more.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">We would love for you to join us as we celebrate everything fun in the kitchen and celebrate home improvement!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">We hope you''ve found this post to be helpful. A range hood, does not need to be just a hood fan..</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Pick the right hood for your kitchen, and it will surely add that major design punch and powerful function that you have been wanting.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">If you are looking into purchasing a range hood and don''t even know where to begin, don''t even worry. Because at Proline Range Hoods we''ve got your back!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Take a peak of our top quality range hood selection over on our site : <a href="http://www.prolinerangehoods.com">www.prolinerangehoods.com</a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Wishing you a splendid Monday and a great rest of your week!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">-Your Friends At Proline</p>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Range Hoods: The Secret Addition For A Beautiful Kitchen', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '823-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-01 22:04:23', '2016-07-01 22:04:23', '', 823, 'http://www.prolinekitchenblog.com/823-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
